(73, 1, 'hrbeu', 14, 'College Introduction', '2009-04-29 06:18:25', '2009-04-29 06:18:25', 'hrbeu', 'College Introduction', 'The College of Power and Energy Engineering open three regular undergraduate programs including: Thermal Power Engineering, Communication and  Transportation, and Marine Engine Engineering.', '<p><strong><span style="font-family: Arial">Introduction</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial">The College of Power and Energy Engineering open three regular undergraduate programs including: Thermal Power Engineering, Communication and&nbsp; Transportation, and Marine Engine Engineering. The College has been authorized to award master degrees in Thermal Power Engineering, Engineering Thermophysics, Fluid Machinery and Engineering, Marine Engine Engineering, Power Machinery and Engineering, Traffic Information Engineering and Control, Refrigeration and Cryogenic Engineering, Chemical Process Equipment, and Environmental Engineering,&nbsp; and doctor degrees in Marine Engine Engineering, and Power Machinery and Engineering. The College also possess its own Postdoctoral R&amp;D Base of Power Energy and Engineering Thermal Physics as well. </span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span style="font-family: Arial">History</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial">Established in 1953, the College of Power and Energy Engineering was once the key branch of Harbin Institute of Military Engineering. After more than 50-year''s development, the College has now become a main base for cultivating talents of marine engineering and power engineering in China.</span><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>', NULL, 177, 1, ''),
(74, 1, 'hrbeu', 14, 'Programs Offered', '2009-04-29 06:20:05', '2009-04-29 06:20:05', 'hrbeu', 'Programs Offered', 'Bachelor in Communication and Transportation\r\nBachelor in Marine Engine Engineering\r\nBachelor in Thermal Power Engineering', '<p><span style="font-family: Arial"><strong>Undergraduate Programs&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong>&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; Bachelor in Communication and Transportation <br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; Bachelor in Marine Engine Engineering <br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; Bachelor in Thermal Power Engineering </span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial"><strong>Postgraduate Programs&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong><br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; Master in Chemical Process Equipment<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; Master in Engineering Thermophysics<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; Master in Environmental Engineering<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; Master in Fluid Machinery and Engineering<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; Master in Marine Engine Engineering<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; Master in Power Machinery and Engineering<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; Master in Refrigeration and Cryogenic Engineering<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; Master in Thermal Energy Engineering<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; Master in Traffic Information Engineering and Control</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial"><strong>PhD Research Fields&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong><br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; Ph.D in Marine Engine Engineering<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; Ph.D in Power Machinery and Engineering</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial"><strong>Postdordorate R&amp;D Bases&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong><br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; Postdoctoral R&amp;D Base in Naval Architecture and Ocean Engineering<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; Postdoctoral R&amp;D Base in Power Energy and Engineering Thermal Physics</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial"><strong>Professional Master of Engineering Programs&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong><br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; Professional Master of Engineering in Communication and Transportation Engineering<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; Professional Master of Engineering in Naval Architecture and Ocean Engineering<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; Professional Master of Engineering in Power Engineering</span></p>', NULL, 184, 1, ''),
(75, 1, 'hrbeu', 14, 'Staff', '2009-04-29 06:20:57', '2009-04-29 06:20:57', 'hrbeu', 'Staff', 'The College of Power and Energy Engineering has a competitive academic team. We have a total of 101 staff, of which 22 professors (including 16 doctoral advisors) and 23 associate professors.', '<p><span style="font-family: Arial">The College of Power and Energy Engineering has a competitive academic team. We have a total of 101 staff, of which 22 professors (including 16 doctoral advisors) and 23 associate professors. Many of the faculty are well-known in the international power engineering arena. There have been more than 3,250 bachelors, masters and doctors graduated from this College.</span></p>', NULL, 117, 1, ''),
(76, 1, 'hrbeu', 14, 'Research', '2009-04-29 06:21:55', '2009-04-29 06:21:55', 'hrbeu', 'Research', 'Our College has strong R&D ability and enjoys a good fame for its distinctive achievements.', '<p><span style="font-family: Arial">Our College has strong R&amp;D ability and enjoys a good fame for its distinctive achievements. During the past years, we have won more than 130 scientific research prizes of national, provincial, and ministerial levels, and have received R&amp;D funds of 45 million yuan RMB&nbsp; in the ''9th Five-year Plan''. Now, during the ''10th Five-year Plan'', we&nbsp; continue to undertake national scientific research projects, with a fund of 200 million yuan RMB. The vigorous research development promotes teaching and the College''s development in other aspects.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial">The College has Internal-combustion Engine Comprehensive Lab, Automobile Application Engineering Lab, and Thermodynamics Lab. The&nbsp; 211 Project'' organized by&nbsp; the Ministry of Education is also sponsoring labs'' construction, and&nbsp; help the College to construct labs of international advanced level. Under such a context, the Power Installing Overall Supervision System, and the Special Power Lab were established.</span></p>', NULL, 106, 1, ''),
