(98, 1, 'hrbeu', 18, 'College Introduction', '2009-04-29 18:50:38', '2009-04-29 18:50:38', 'hrbeu', 'College Introduction', 'The College of Mechanical and Electrical Engineering is one of the first established colleges of the University. ', '<p><span style="font-family: Arial"><strong>Introduction: </strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial">The College of Mechanical and Electrical Engineering is one of the first established colleges of the University. The College offers 2 undergraduate programs, including Mechanical Design Manufacture and its&nbsp; Automation, and Industry Design (Science and Engineering). It has been authorized to award master''s degrees in Mechanical Design and Theory, Mechanical Manufacture and its&nbsp; Automation, Mechatronic Engineering, Vehicle Engineering, and Artistic Design; it can also confer 2 doctoral degrees in Mechatronic Engineering, and Mechanical&nbsp; Design and Theory.</span></p>', NULL, 162, 1, ''),
(99, 1, 'hrbeu', 18, 'Programs Offered', '2009-04-29 18:51:33', '2009-04-29 18:51:33', 'hrbeu', 'Programs Offered', 'Undergraduate Programs     \r\nBachelor in Industrial Design (Science and Engineering) \r\nBachelor in Mechanical Design Manufacture and its Automation', '<p><span style="font-family: Arial"><strong>Undergraduate Programs&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong><br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; Bachelor in Industrial Design (Science and Engineering) <br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; Bachelor in Mechanical Design Manufacture and its Automation</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial"><strong>Postgraduate Programs&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong>&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; Master in Artistic Design<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; Master in Mechanical Design and Theory<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; Master in Mechanical Manufacture and its Automation<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; Master in Mechatronic Engineering<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; Master in Vehicle Engineering</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial"><strong>PhD Research Fields&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\n</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp; Ph.D in Mechanical Design and Theory<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; Ph.D in Mechanical Engineering</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial"><strong>Postdordorate R&amp;D Bases&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong><br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; Postdoctoral R&amp;D Base in Control Science and Engineering<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; Postdoctoral R&amp;D Base in Mechanical Engineering<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; Postdoctoral R&amp;D Base in Mechanics </span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial"><strong>Professional Master of Engineering Programs&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; Professional Master of Engineering in Industrial Engineering<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; Professional Master of Engineering in Mechanical Engineering</span></p>', NULL, 205, 1, ''),
(100, 1, 'hrbeu', 18, 'Staff', '2009-04-29 18:52:11', '2009-04-29 18:52:11', 'hrbeu', 'Staff', 'The College of Mechanical and Electrical Engineering has competitive faculty.', '<p><span style="font-family: Arial">The College of Mechanical and Electrical Engineering has competitive faculty. There are 115 staff, 18 professors (including 9 doctoral advisors), and 28 associate professors. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial">For many years, this College has been undertaking many science researches, including the projects under the ''863 National Project'', some supported by the National Natural Science Fund, and several provincial and ministerial key projects. The faculty has gained substantial achievements for research, and won more than 90 national and provincial prizes. The faculty has published more than 860 papers and 55 academic monographs published in home and abroad. This College owns a complete set of experiment equipments and grasp advanced testing methods, in which the Advanced Production Technology Lab is the training base for the national CAD training network. In the ''211 Project'', its two disciplines have gained the support as a national key constructing project.</span></p>', NULL, 120, 1, ''),
(101, 1, 'hrbeu', 18, 'Research', '2009-04-29 18:52:51', '2009-04-29 18:52:51', 'hrbeu', 'Research', 'The College of Mechanical and Electrical Engineering has 20 years'' experience in undertaking national key R&D programs and has formed a R&D team with strong competence.', '<p><span style="font-family: Arial">The College of Mechanical and Electrical Engineering has 20 years'' experience in undertaking national key R&amp;D programs and has formed a R&amp;D team with strong competence. In the recent years, the College attaches more importance to the researching and developing of civilian products, to serve the national economy and the local development. With more than 2,000,000 yuan RMB as R&amp;D fund, the College has obtained great achievements in both military supplies research, and civilian areas. Since 1990, the College has altogether gained one National Scientific and Technology Progress Awards and 35 Provincial Scientific and Technology Progress Awards.</span></p>', NULL, 111, 1, '');
