"Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US">Information and Computer Science</span></font></b></td>\r\n            <td><font size="2" face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US">0086 451 82519384</span></font></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td width="270"><b><font size="2" face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US">Probability and Statistics </span></font></b></td>\r\n            <td><font size="2" face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US">0086 451 82519384</span></font></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td width="270"><b><font size="2" face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US">Foundational Mathematics and Application</span></font></b></td>\r\n            <td><font size="2" face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US">0086 451 82519384</span></font></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td width="270"><b><font size="2" face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US">Experimental Base of Mathematics Modeling</span></font></b></td>\r\n            <td><font size="2" face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US">0086 451 82519384</span></font></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td width="270"><b><font size="2" face="Times New Roman">Administration Office</font></b></td>\r\n            <td><font size="2" face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US">0086 451 82519754</span></font></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td width="270"><b><font size="2" face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-GB">Location</span></font></b></td>\r\n            <td><font size="2" face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US">The 2nd Floor, No.11 Building</span></font></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</p>', NULL, 99, 1, ''),
(127, 1, 'hrbeu', 23, 'Department Introduction', '2009-04-29 19:14:29', '2009-04-29 19:14:29', 'hrbeu', 'Department Introduction', 'Foreign Languages Department offers the teaching of the following languages: ', '<p><strong><span style="font-family: Arial">Introduction: </span></strong></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial">Foreign Languages Department offers the teaching of the following languages: English, Russia, German, French, Japanese and Korean (including the first foreign language and the second foreign language), which is conducted at undergraduate, postgraduate, and doctoral levels and covers the common foreign language teaching tasks of about 16,000 non-English major undergraduate students, approximately 6,000 non-English major postgraduate students and doctoral students. The Department also provides one English major bachelor program: English, two English major master programs: English Language &amp; Literature, Foreign Linguistics &amp; Applied Linguistics, and has a full-time enrolment of over 117 postgraduate students and 343 undergraduate students. In the Test of English for Majors Band 4 of recent four years, the English major undergraduates of the Department have achieved a 100% pass rate, which takes the leading position among the Universities in China.</span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span style="font-family: Arial">Facilities:</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial">Foreign Languages Department has one multimedia language lab center comprising 180-seat multimedia language lab and 2,140-seat multimedia language labs, one foreign language radio station which can broadcast programs of different languages simultaneously, one CAI section and one library collecting more than 8,200 reference books and journals of English, Russian, Japanese, German, French, etc., and abundant of audio-visual materials.<br />\r\n</span></p>', NULL, 136, 1, ''),
(128, 1, 'hrbeu', 23, 'Programs Offered', '2009-04-29 19:15:07', '2009-04-29 19:15:07', 'hrbeu', 'Programs Offered', 'Undergraduate Programs     \r\nBachelor in English ', '<p><strong><span style="font-family: Arial">Undergraduate Programs&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></strong><span style="font-family: Arial"><br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; Bachelor in English </span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span style="font-family: Arial">Postgraduate Programs&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></strong><span style="font-family: Arial"><br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; Master in English Language and Literature<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; Master in Linguistics and Applied Linguistics in Foreign Languages </span></p>', NULL, 125, 1, ''),
(129, 1, 'hrbeu', 23, 'Staff', '2009-04-29 19:15:42', '2009-04-29 19:15:42', 'hrbeu', 'Staff', 'Foreign Languages Department has a teaching and administrative staff of 130 members. ', '<p><span style="font-family: Arial">Foreign Languages Department has a teaching and administrative staff of 130 members. The Department has a faculty with academic prestige and educational experience, consisting of 8 professors, 41 associate professors, 31 lecturers, and 38 assistant teachers. Among the faculty members, there are 22 advisors for master students, 76 teachers with master��s degree, 4 doctoral candidates, 16 master candidates, and over 30 members have finished overseas study and research. They report constant achievements in academic research and foreign language teaching. Their academic papers, books, textbooks and reference books have won many an award in national and provincial appraisal.</span></p>', NULL, 117, 1, ''),
(130, 1, 'hrbeu', 23, 'Research', '2009-04-29 19:16:15', '2009-04-29 19:16:15', 'hrbeu', 'Research', 'Foreign Languages Department encourages faculty members to engage in researches in pedagogy, academic and curriculum programs.', '<p><span style="font-family: Arial">Foreign Languages Department encourages faculty members to engage in researches in pedagogy, academic and curriculum programs. The faculty has always obtained funding and support from the Education Ministry and the University. The faculty members are active in writing academic papers, participating in academic meetings and have played an important role in college/university English teaching in Heilongjiang Province. For instance, through reforming the traditional teaching modes and exploring new pedagogy constantly, the Department has established a series of effective teaching methods for students to meet the new challenges in the contemporary society and has kept organizing and encouraging activities of teaching and research, such as classroom-teaching demonstration, discussion of teaching methods, etc.. Based on these efforts, the Department has made outstanding achievements in foreign language teaching, especially in increasing the efficiency of classroom teaching.</span></p>', NULL, 99, 1, ''),
(131, 1, 'hrbeu', 23, 'Contact us', '2009-04-29 19:16:46', '2009-04-29 19:16:46', 'hrbeu', 'Contact us', 'Contact us', '<p>\r\n<table id="table1" border="1" width="100%">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td width="44%"><b><font size="2" face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US">Dean</span></font></b></td>\r\n            <td width="53%"><font size="2" face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US">0086 451 82519226</span></font></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td rowspan="2" width="44%"><b><font size="2" face="Times New Roman">Deputy Dean</font></b></td>\r\n            <td width="53%"><font size="2" face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US">0086 451 825</span></font><span lang="en-us"><font size="2" face="Times New Roman">69619</font></span></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td width="53%"><font size="2" face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US">0086 451 82519226</span></font></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><b><font size="2" face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US">German and Japanese Language Unit</span></font></b></td>\r\n            <td width="53%"><font size="2" face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US">0086 451 82519697</span></font></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><b><font size="2" face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US">Japanese, Russian, German Languages Unit</span></font></b></td>\r\n            <td width="53%"><font size="2" face="Times New Roman">0086 451 82519697</font></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><b><font size="2" face="Times New Roman">Language Lab</font></b></td>\r\n            <td width="53%"><font size="2" face="Times New Roman">0086 451 82519366</font></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><b><font size="2" face="Times New Roman">Foreign Language Radio Broadcasting Station</font></b></td>\r\n            <td width="53%"><font size="2" face="Times New Roman">0086 451 82519366</font></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><b><font size="2" face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US">Administration Office</span></font></b></td>\r\n            <td width="53%"><font size="2" face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US">0086 451 82519595</span></font></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><b><font size="2" face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-GB">Location </span></font></b></td>\r\n            <td><font size="2" face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US">4th Floor, </span></font><span lang="en-us"><font size="2" face="Times New Roman">Basic Teaching Experimental Building</font></span></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</p>', NULL, 100, 1, ''),
(132, 1, 'hrbeu', 24, 'College Introduction', '2009-04-29 19:17:31', '2009-04-29 19:17:31', 'hrbeu', 'College Introduction', 'The College of Humanities and Social Sciences developed from the faculty of Marxism-Leninism, ', '<p><span style="font-family: Arial">The College of Humanities and Social Sciences developed from the faculty of Marxism-Leninism, Harbin Military Engineering Institute. It has been playing an important role in cultivating students and training personnel in the past 5 decades, especially since the establishment of the market-oriented economic systems. The College consists of 5 departments, 2 research centers, 10 teaching and research sections, and an information center with 100,000 books, 100 kinds of academic periodicals, together with an electronic reading room in which there are 30 computers. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial">Great academic achievements have been attained in the past 3 years. The College has won National Level Excellent Teaching Prize three times, Provincial Level Excellent Teaching Prize six times. The staff has published 32 monographs and 286 academic papers, receiving financial aids many times from National Social Sciences Founding, Education Ministry Key Project Founding, and Heilongjiang Province Project Founding.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial">The College has the authorities to award PhD degree in Education in Ideology and Politics, Master degrees in Marxist Theory, Political Theory, Science of Economic Law, Sociology, and also Bachelor degrees in Politics and Administration, Education in Ideology and Politics, Law.</span></p>', NULL, 101, 1, ''),
(133, 1, 'hrbeu', 24, 'Programs Offered', '2009-04-29 19:18:17', '2009-05-08 23:10:37', 'hrbeu', 'Programs Offered', 'Undergraduate Programs     \r\nBachelor in Education in Ideology and Politics\r\nBachelor in Law', '<p><strong>Undergraduate Programs&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong>&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; <a href="http://englisha.hrbeu.edu.cn/showarticle.php?articleid=353">Bachelor in Education in Ideology and Politics</a><br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; Bachelor in Law<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; Bachelor in Politics and Public Administration</p>\r\n<p><strong>Postgraduate Programs&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong><br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; Master in Applied Psychology<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; Master in Marxism Theory<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; Master in Political Theory<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; Master in Science of Economic Laws<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; Master in Sociology</p>\r\n<p><strong>PhD Research Fields&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\n</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp; Ph.D in Education in Ideology and Politics</p>', NULL, 102, 1, ''),
(134, 1, 'hrbeu', 24, 'Staff', '2009-04-29 19:18:44', '2009-04-29 19:18:44', 'hrbeu', 'Staff', 'The College has a staff of 87, including 13 professors, 34 associate professors,', '<p><span style="font-family: Arial">The College has a staff of 87, including 13 professors, 34 associate professors, 28 lecturers and administrators and assistant teachers. 8 of them are PhDs, 53 are Masters, and 18 doctoral candidates. They are now teaching 150 classes, covering the fields of humanities and social sciences, both for the undergraduates and postgraduates.</span></p>', NULL, 96, 1, '');
