(135, 1, 'hrbeu', 24, 'Research', '2009-04-29 19:19:12', '2009-04-29 19:19:12', 'hrbeu', 'Research', 'A series of policies have been set up to stimulate the staff to work creatively in academic research at the College.', '<p><span style="font-family: Arial">A series of policies have been set up to stimulate the staff to work creatively in academic research at the College. This has made a good foundation for the achievements of academic research. In the past 3 years, the College has won National Level Excellent Teaching Prize three times, and Provincial Level Excellent Teaching Prize six times. Its staff has published 32 monographs and 286 academic papers, receiving financial aids many times from National Social Sciences Founding, Education Ministry Key Project Founding, and Heilongjiang Province Project Founding. All together, the College staff have won 87 prizes of various kinds.<br />\r\n</span></p>', NULL, 102, 1, ''),
