(137, 1, 'hrbeu', 28, 'Department Introduction', '2009-04-29 19:21:06', '2009-04-29 19:30:16', 'hrbeu', 'Department Introduction', 'The Physical Education Department was set up in 1987, mainly undertaking the entire school physical education tasks,', '<p><span style="font-family: Arial">The Physical Education Department was set up in 1987, mainly undertaking the entire school physical education tasks, organizing sports competition and scientific research in the related areas. The Department organized to Establish the university student sports association in 1995, which has developed 17 single items sports teams. The Department also holds track and field games, the sports culture festival every year to enhance campus culture, whose attendance reaches 70,000 people every year. Under the faculty''s hard work, the University''s pass rate in the national University student physique healthy tests maintains 98% or higher. The Department was awarded with the National Sports Work Advanced Unit by the National Sports Bureau.</span></p>', NULL, 97, 1, ''),
(138, 1, 'hrbeu', 28, 'Programs Offered', '2009-04-29 19:21:35', '2009-04-29 19:30:10', 'hrbeu', 'Programs Offered', 'Postgraduate Programs     \r\n   Master in Theory of Sports Pedagogy and Training', '<p><strong><span>Postgraduate Programs&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></strong><span><br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; Master in Theory of Sports Pedagogy and Training</span></p>\r\n<p><span>In 2003, the Department was authorized to establish the master program in sports education and training study. The Department has formulated a complete teaching plan, and program instruction. The program has five specialized directions in speed skating, basketball, swimming, school sports study, and physiology of exercise. In 2004, the sports training department recruited&nbsp; 5 students&nbsp; for the first session, and 10 for 2005. At present, the academic education has attained certain level, and the faculty has explored some practical and creative teaching method. The faculty strength is being strengthened with more experiences accumulated.<br />\r\n</span></p>', NULL, 101, 1, ''),
(139, 1, 'hrbeu', 28, 'Staff', '2009-04-29 19:22:53', '2009-04-29 19:30:02', 'hrbeu', 'Staff', 'The Department has 71 academic and administrative staff,  including 5 professor  people, and 19 associate professor.', '<p><span style="font-family: Arial">The Department has 71 academic and administrative staff,&nbsp; including 5 professor&nbsp; people, and 19 associate professor (20 teachers having master and doctorate degrees).&nbsp; In 2003 the Department established the master program of sports education and training study in the specializing directions of&nbsp; speed skating, the basketball, the swimming, the school sports study, the physiology of exercise.</span></p>', NULL, 89, 1, ''),
(140, 1, 'hrbeu', 28, 'Research', '2009-04-29 19:23:18', '2009-04-29 19:29:53', 'hrbeu', 'Research', 'In 2005 HEU''s physical education curriculum was evaluated as the provincial high-quality curriculum.', '<p style="text-justify: inter-ideograph; text-align: justify; layout-grid-mode: char"><span style="font-family: Arial"><span lang="EN-US">In 2005 HEU''s physical education curriculum was evaluated as the provincial high-quality curriculum. The scientific research work obtains the unprecedented progress, in the recent five years, the faculty has publish </span><span lang="EN-US">326 </span><span lang="EN-US">papers in all levels of academic publications, </span><span lang="EN-US">35</span><span lang="EN-US"> teaching material, and </span><span lang="EN-US">7</span><span lang="EN-US">audio and video teaching materials. The Department was awarded with </span><span lang="EN-US">two provincial </span><span lang="EN-US">first awards, and </span><span lang="EN-US">three</span><span lang="EN-US"> second-level awards.</span></span></p>', NULL, 97, 1, ''),
