(177, 1, 'hrbeu', 4, 'Foreign Teacher Apartment', '2009-04-30 00:09:39', '2009-04-30 00:09:39', 'hrbeu', 'Foreign Teacher Apartment', 'Foreign Teacher Apartment', '<p>Each foreign teacher is supplied with an apartment&nbsp; includes at least one bedroom, one living room, one bathroom, and kitchen/cooking area. The kitchen is well ventilated for cooking and equipped with a refrigerator, stove, water dispenser, and microwave oven.</p>\r\n<p align="justify">The bathroom includes a western style toilet, a shower (with a water heater) and a sink. <br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align="justify">The apartment is furnished with the following items: bed, dresser, wardrobe, desk and chair, proper lighting, bookshelf, sofa, easy chairs, tea table, television, IDD telephone, heating system, floor fans, washing machine, direct Internet hook-up.</p>', NULL, 270, 1, ''),
