(181, 1, 'hrbeu', 4, 'Internet Service', '2009-04-30 00:11:56', '2009-04-30 00:11:56', 'hrbeu', 'Internet Service', 'Internet Service', '<p align="justify" style="line-height: 150%">Internet services are provided by the university for students use.</p>\r\n<p align="justify" style="line-height: 150%"><b>When applying for a new internet account:</b></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p align="justify" style="line-height: 150%">Please register with the Network Information Center&nbsp; (Rm. 302, Shaw Building)</p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p align="justify" style="line-height: 150%">Please&nbsp; pay 100 yuan RMB, and&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 150%; text-align: justify">you will be asked to show: your Student ID Card, and one photocopy of your passport.</p>\r\n    </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 21pt; text-indent: -21pt; line-height: 150%; text-align: justify">Note: Please take good care of the receipt, and note that the&nbsp; phone number provided in case of any internet errors.</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<p align="justify" style="line-height: 150%"><b>Monthly Service Accounts:</b> please pay at the Phone Credit Booth&nbsp;(No. 9 Student Apartment Building).</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 150%; text-align: justify"><b>Internet Card Accounts:</b> please arrange your top-up at the HEU Network Information Center (Rm. 406, Shaw Building).<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>', NULL, 206, 1, ''),
