(184, 1, 'hrbeu', 4, 'Recreation Center', '2009-04-30 00:13:35', '2009-04-30 00:13:35', 'hrbeu', 'Recreation Center', 'Recreation Center', '<p class="MsoNormal" align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">HEU has an 8,800m<sup>2 </sup>and a 3,500m<sup>2</sup> indoor gyms. Both include a swimming pool, table tennis room, exercise room, aerobic exercise room, practice room, contest court, badminton court, tennis court, sepak takraw court and kung fu court. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe outdoor playfield comprises of 2 standard athletic fields, 5 football fields, 28 basketball courts, 12 volleyball courts, 4 tennis courts, 2 beach volleyball courts, 1 handball court, 1 baseball field, and 1 croquet court. </span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">With many fun things to do in an atmosphere that promotes relaxation, the sports center is certainly one of the students'' favorite places on campus. </span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" align="justify">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" align="justify">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p class="MsoNormal" align="justify"><b><span lang="EN-US">Swimming Card Application Service for New Students</span></b></p>\r\n    </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">All sports members require a physical examination certificate issued by the University Hospital. With the certificate the students can apply for a&nbsp; swimming card in the gym. Please apply for the card before the first PE class of the semester. The card will need to be filled out and have a photo attached, then the gym will have it stamped and plastic-filmed.</span></p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p class="MsoNormal" align="left"><b><span lang="EN-US">Lost Card Service</span></b></p>\r\n    </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" align="justify" style="margin-left: 0px"><span lang="EN-US">Once your card is lost, you will be given a replacement at presenting of a reapplication report sealed by your department, your student card, examination-admission card, and a one-inch photo.</span></p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p class="MsoNormal" align="justify"><b><span lang="EN-US">Court Renting Service</span></b></p>\r\n    </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" align="justify" style="margin-left: 0px"><span lang="EN-US">Any court within the gym can be rented from Monday to Friday by a college, a department or a class as the smallest unit. </span></p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p class="MsoNormal" align="justify"><span lang="EN-US"><b>Opening Hours</b></span></p>\r\n    </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div align="center">\r\n<table id="table1" width="91%" border="1">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td width="44%"><b><span lang="en-us"><font size="2">Courts</font></span></b></td>\r\n            <td width="15%"><b><font size="2">Services</font></b></td>\r\n            <td width="15%"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-weight: 700; color: black"><font size="2">Time</font></span></td>\r\n            <td width="21%"><b><span lang="en-us"><font size="2">Opening Hours</font></span></b></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td width="44%" rowspan="3"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-weight: 700; color: black"><font size="2">Practice Room</font></span></td>\r\n            <td width="15%"><font size="2">Student</font></td>\r\n            <td width="15%">\r\n            <p class="MsoNormal" align="justify" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px"><span lang="EN-US" style="color: black"><font size="2">18:00 - 20:00</font></span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width="21%" rowspan="3"><span lang="en-us"><font size="2">Weekday&nbsp; evening and the whole day during weekends</font></span></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td width="15%"><font size="2">Staff</font></td>\r\n            <td width="15%"><span lang="EN-US" style="color: bla