rmal" style="margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 150%; text-align: justify"><span style="font-family: Arial">Tel: 0086 451 82519695 </span></p>\r\n</blockquote>', NULL, 172, 1, ''),
(187, 1, 'hrbeu', 7, 'Commitment', '2009-04-30 00:25:12', '2009-04-30 00:25:12', 'hrbeu', 'Commitment', 'Commitment', '<p>HEU is making unremitting efforts to connect with and learn from the international world. To further raise the university''s teaching and research levels, HEU has attracted respected universities both nationally and internationally, to join in the construction of a high-tech research and software center.</p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">Moreover, HEU is actively developing exchange and cooperative relationships with academic institutions in other countries and across China.&nbsp; These along with other cooperative efforts, not only add to the strength of the HEU academic staff, but also enhance and economically benefit a variety of disciplines and departments.</span></p>', NULL, 918, 1, ''),
