(190, 1, 'hrbeu', 7, 'Exchange programs', '2009-04-30 00:26:43', '2009-04-30 00:26:43', 'hrbeu', 'Exchange programs', 'Exchange programs', '<h2 align="justify"><font size="3"><b><span lang="EN-US">JUSST program between </span></b>t</font><b><font size="3">he University of Electro-Communications, Japan and </font></b><span lang="EN-US"><b><font size="3">HEU</font></b></span></h2>\r\n<p align="justify">It is a short-term Exchange Study Program for senior undergraduate students (3rd year or higher) and postgraduate students in the areas of Science, Engineering &amp; Technology.</p>\r\n<p align="justify">JUSST program is a part of UEC''s international collaboration programs for students and staff to enhance educational understanding and cooperation through Science, Technology and Culture. This JUSST program can help students to learn science and engineering at UEC without interrupting their ongoing major studies at the home institution. The students may transfer credit for studies successfully completed at UEC towards the degree at their home institution.</p>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<h2 align="justify"><font size="2">Courses: Science/Engineering &amp; Technology</font></h2>\r\n<h2 align="justify"><font size="2"><b><span lang="EN-US">HEU Consulting Office: </span></b></font><font size="3"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-weight: 400; color: black">Foreign Affairs Office</span></font></h2>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US" style="color: black"><b><font size="2">Email:</font></b> <a href="mailto:gochdi@public.pr.pl.cn">heufao@vip.0451.com </a></span></p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<p align="justify" style="line-height: 18pt"><b>The Programs of the College of International Cooperative Education , HEU</b></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p align="justify"><font style="font-weight: 700"><span lang="EN-US">Marine Engineering: </span></font></p>\r\n    </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">This Program is going to train students who have the following qualities: all around developed, scientifically interested, knowledgeable in international field of Ocean Engineering, well trained in the field of naval architecture.</span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">HEU and the University of Strathclyde, both parties, make teaching plan and administrate altogether. In the first and second year, students finish their basic subjects and at the same time they learn English Intensively. In the third and forth year they learn their core subjects.</span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">This Program includes mechanic principles, ocean engineering system, shipping machines, shipping control and so on. It puts great emphasis to theory and practice and follows the development of the field of ocean engineering. The graduates can work in the area of ship construction, shipping power factory or research center, ship power design and ship maintenance. </span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">The students are taught in the Chinese and Western ways. On the basis of ocean engineering, the students can also learn some subjects of English department. In this way, the students will not only master their specialized subject but also be good at English. They know different cultures and they are all around developed. </span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">Major subjects: English, mathematics, computer, professional subjects.</span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">The university of Strathclyde offers some professional subjects.</span></p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-weight: 700">Finance: </span></p>\r\n    </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">This Program is going to train students who have the following qualities: all around developed, scientifically interested, knowledgeable in international field of international finance, well trained in the field of finance.</span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">HEU and the University of Strathclyde, both parties, make teaching plan and administrate altogether. In the first and second year, students finish their basic subjects and at the same time they learn English Intensively. In the third and forth year they learn their core subjects.</span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">This Program includes the basic knowledge in finance, such as bank, investment, insurance, settlement etc. It puts great emphasis to theory and practice and follows the development of the field of finance. The graduates can work in the area of bank, investment, insurance, settlement etc. and they can work in the state owned companies to do relative jobs. </span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">The students are taught in the Chinese and Western way. On the basis of finance, the students can also learn some subjects of English department. In this way, the students will not only master their specialized subject but also be good at English. They know different cultures and they are all around developed. </span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">Major subjects: English, mathematics, computer, professional subjects.</span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">The university of Strathclyde offers some professional subjects.</span></p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="en-us">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-GB" style="color: #333399"><a onclick="javascript:change(''International Co-ed College'',''/Academic_Departments/International_Coeducation_College/College_Introduction.html'')" href="http://english.hrbeu.edu.cn/information.jsp?id=358&amp;exid=359&amp;asd=a#"><u>To learn more about the</u></a><u> </u><a onclick="javascript:change(''International Co-ed College'',''/Academic_Departments/International_Coeducation_College/College_Introduction.html'')" href="http://english.hrbeu.edu.cn/information.jsp?id=358&amp;exid=359&amp;asd=a#"><u>programs offered by the College</u></a><u> of</u><a onclick="javascript:change(''International Co-ed College'',''/Academic_Departments/International_Coeducation_College/College_Introduction.html'')" href="http://english.hrbeu.edu.cn/information.jsp?id=358&amp;exid=359&amp;asd=a#"><u> International Cooperative Education </u></a></span></p>', NULL, 971, 1, ''),
(191, 1, 'hrbeu', 7, 'College of International Coopeartive Education', '2009-04-30 00:27:25', '2009-06-30 10:35:34', 'hrbeu', 'College of International Coopeartive Education', 'College of International Coopeartive Education', '<p style="text-align: right"><span style="font-size: larger"><b><span lang="EN-GB"><a href="http://heucice.hrbeu.edu.cn/">College Homepage</a></span></b></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify"><span style="font-size: larger"><b><span lang="EN-GB">Introduction: </span></b></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify"><span style="font-size: larger"><span lang="EN-US" style="color: #373737">In order to adapt well to internationalized education trend nowadays, in 2003 HEU set up the College of International Cooperative Education&nbsp; (ICEC). There are two purposes to set up a college like this. One is to cooperate with well-known universities abroad and develop bachelor degree co-education; the other is to assume the responsibility of Chinese language education to overseas students and their daily affairs management.<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\nCurrently, ICEC has cooperation respectively with New England University in Australia, Strathclyde University in UK, and State Marine Technical University of St.Petersburg in Russia. The cooperation is in the form of ''2+2'' bachelor degree education program. ICEC upholds the belief of ''integrate foreign high-quality education resource, draw on foreign advanced education ideology, assimilate foreign excellent academic content, realize rigorous and standard management, and cultivate international intellectual and professional talents''. ICEC attaches importance to education management, language training, academic materials selection, faculty training and course building. Primary teaching method for the courses is in the form of bilingual education. Some courses even have matched original foreign materials. In this way, besides the teaching of major courses of the cooperation program, the bilingual education and foreign exchange can be greatly promoted. Therefore, the co-education program is highly appraised by the Heilongjiang Provincial Chinese-foreign cooperation program inspection group. The inspection group holds the view that the international co-education pattern of HEU focuses on social benefits, recruits students of key level in the national college entrance examination, so the construction of the program is mature and has realistic popularization significance.</span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" align="justify"><span style="font-size: larger"><span lang="EN-US">ICEC is responsible for the organization and implementation of Chinese teaching, daily management of students, as well as management of overseas student''s apartment and foreign teacher''s management. At present, ICEC has the received the overseas students from Japan, Korea, UK, Canada, India, Nepal, Pakistan, Thailand, Russia and so on. ICEC has established an experienced and well structural teaching team, developed exchange activity of Chinese training, and researched theory of Chinese teaching. ICEC has built an ease and joyful atmosphere of studying for the students in line with open teaching idea and student-oriented teaching model. According to the different demand and different Chinese level of overseas students in Chinese teaching, we have designed 5 level Chinese course (A, B, C, D, E) which is progressives and link up mutually. The teachers will not only pay the attention to strengthening communicated ability and training of reading ability but also overall promotion of Chinese level.</span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" align="justify"><span style="font-size: larger"><span lang="EN-US">&nbsp;ICEC has built the language labs, multimedia rooms only for the overseas students, at the same time, has an overseas apartment&nbsp; which includes kitchen, bathroom, satellite TV, refrigerator, washing machine, water heater, telephone, wide band connection with the excellent environment, full facilities and high-quality service. The college organizes the overseas student to carry out the richly colorful activities frequently in order to make them experience the Chinese culture in the process of studying.</span></span></p>', NULL, 956, 1, ''),
(192, 1, 'hrbeu', 7, 'Foreign Affairs Office', '2009-04-30 00:29:26', '2009-04-30 00:29:26', 'hrbeu', 'Foreign Affairs Office', 'Foreign Affairs Office', '<p><font face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US">\r\n<p align="justify"><font style="font-weight: 700">Introduction:<a name="A"></a></font></p>\r\n<p>Foreign Affairs Office of Harbin Engineering University is a department, which manages and serves the University''s foreign cooperation and exchange work.&nbsp; The Office is responsible for implementing national foreign policies and higher authority departments to help guide and coordinate the university''s external affairs. The function of the Office is to enhance the international reputation of the University in all aspects, including teaching, scientific research, industrial development, and rear service. It serves to also recruit experienced students and employees from foreign countries to help enhance the strength of the academic departments of the University. The main functions can be generalized as the follows:</p>\r\n</span></font></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p align="justify">managing and assisting international collaborations</p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p align="justify">organizing&nbsp; international exchanges</p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p align="justify">organizing international lectures/seminars/conferences, etc.</p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p align="justify">procedure for long/short term travels abroad handle for both students and University staff.</p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p align="justify">enrolling and organizing foreign students and foreign affairs.</p>\r\n    </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><b><span lang="EN-US">\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US"><b>Sections:<a name="B"></a></b></span></p>\r\n<p>International Communications</p>\r\n<b><b>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</b></b></span></b></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">&nbsp;in charge of :</span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">inviting, reception, arranging and organizing of the visiting foreign guests;</span></p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">communicating for and implementing international exchange programs; </span></p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">examining, and issuing approvals for the academic departments'' application to host international conferences, and coordinating international conferences held at HEU;&nbsp; </span></p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">examining and issuing approvals for international visits, and issuing approvals of all official foreign business, including: application management of the passport and visa paperwork etc.&nbsp; </span></p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">managing international exchange programs with other academic institutions. </span></p>\r\n    </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p align="justify"><b><span lang="EN-US">International Students </span></b></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">&nbsp;in charge of :</span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">enrollment of foreign students, and management of foreign students'' register record;&nbsp; </span></p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">management of foreign students'' passports and visas;&nbsp; </span></p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">administration of&nbsp; foreign students;&nbsp; </span></p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">logistics support for the foreign student apartment;&nbsp; </span></p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">international training item;&nbsp; </span></p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">establishing the study abroad center.</span></p>\r\n    </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p align="justify"><b><span lang="EN-US">Administration&nbsp; Section</span></b></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">&nbsp;in charge of :</span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">recruiting and coordinating foreign experts;&nbsp; </span></p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">applying for and administrating short- and long-term program funds from the State Administration on Foreign Experts Affairs and the Chinese Commission of Science, Commission of Science Technology and Industry for National Defense;&nbsp; </span></p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">applying for and administrating the Hong Kong and Macao education funds;&nbsp; </span></p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">managing foreign language training programs for HEU faculty;&nbsp; </span></p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">daily office routine work and work automation.</span></p>\r\n    </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p align="justify">　<span lang="EN-US"><a href="http://english.hrbeu.edu.cn/information.jsp?id=358&amp;exid=365&amp;asd=a#top">Back to Top</a></span></p>\r\n<p><span lang="EN-US">\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-weight: 700">Contacts us:<a name="C"></a></span></p>\r\n<p>Address:&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p><span lang="en-us"><font face="Times New Roman">Rm 427 &amp; 431, Administration Building, </font></span><font face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US">145 Nantong Street,Nangang District, Harbin, China&nbsp; </span></font></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">Telephones:&nbsp; 0086 0451 82519213,82518267,82568267,and 82568266 </span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">Fax:&nbsp; 0086 451 82530010,82568288 </span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">Zip code:&nbsp; 150001&nbsp; </span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">E-mail:&nbsp; 