(194, 1, 'hrbeu', 8, 'Brief', '2009-04-30 00:30:41', '2009-04-30 00:30:41', 'hrbeu', 'Brief', 'Brief', '<div class="Section1" style="layout-grid:  15.6pt none">\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">Harbin Engineering University is a state key university, which attaches priority to engineering while combining with disciplines of science, management, arts, law and economics together.</span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">During the ''10<sup>th</sup> Five-year Plan'', HEU has developed rapidly in the scientific research fields of shipping, ocean defense, ocean development and nuclear energy application by exploiting its technical advantages, which have also become the important support for its discipline construction.</span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">HEU began to be listed as one of the state key universities in 1978. It has trained more than 60,000 graduates up till now, many of whom have become main force in all walks of life. Now the University has 2 state key laboratories, 1 national education and training base of electrical engineering and electronics, 6 provincial and ministry-level key laboratories, 52 professional and basic laboratories. And there are more than 1,600 technical personnel, among whom 5 academicians of Chinese Academy of Engineering. </span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">Through years of research, HEU leads domestically and occupies advanced level internationally in underwater robot technology, shipping anti-rolling technology, dynamic positioning, navigation technology, acoustic positioning, and nuclear power simulation etc. The scientific research advances forwarded at an amazing speed&nbsp; since the ''10<sup>th</sup> Five-year Plan''. The University is receiving research funding allocated from government up to 230 million in 2004.</span></p>\r\n</div>', NULL, 866, 1, '');
