(195, 1, 'hrbeu', 8, 'Research and Development', '2009-04-30 00:31:06', '2009-04-30 00:31:06', 'hrbeu', 'Research and Development', 'Research and Development', '<p align="justify"><b><span lang="EN-US">Ships and Vessels Technology</span></b></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">This research unit contains many highly experienced engineering experts and theorists, whose expertise in modern ship structure design and ship fluid mechanics has meant great development in designing, and research. </span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">Thanks to the loan form the World Bank and the support form the 211 Project, the international and domestic first-class research test installations have been completed. Today the research unit is undertaking various ship designing tasks, and also various ocean wave state ship model tests, ship structure tests, fluid power tests and computer simulation tests etc.</span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><b><span lang="EN-US">Power Engineering Technology</span></b></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">HEU has a large group of experts who are engaged in power engineering research, development and designing. They have successively developed dozens of technical achievements in power engineering, such as diesel engine electronic speed adjustment, exhaust and noise elimination, diesel oil and fuel combined car, plasma ignition, desalination of sea water, boiler smoke and exhaust energy retrieve technique and thermal energy and electricity conversion etc. </span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">Owing to the technical forces, advanced equipments and methods, and the experienced expert team, the research unit is able to take on and tackle various power engineering difficulties and provide solutions.</span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><b><span lang="EN-US">Automation Engineering</span></b></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">This research unit has been designed and developed to include research in: comprehensive utilization of medical information, realization of informationization, intelligence and automation for medical treatment, networking, informationization, automation transformation for different industrial processes, research, development and designing of electric power propulsion, AC-DC conversion, power factor compensation; control technique of horizon shipping submersible and automatic operation. </span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><b><span lang="EN-US">Underwater Acoustic Engineering</span></b></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">The Underwater Acoustic Engineering Research Unit concentrates on: tracking, surveying, speed-measuring, position-finding, identification of various underwater objectives, the transmission of underwater digitalized information (images) by underwater technology. We have already developed more than 10 sets of hydroacoustic testing and measuring devices which meet different requirements from clients, some of the techniques have won state, provincial and ministry-level science and technology progressive prizes. Underwater acoustic engineering belongs to state key discipline with a state key laboratory. </span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">The research unit consists of renowned experts and professors in the fields. All of whom can can undertake the tasks of complicated difficult underwater acoustic measuring and the development of experiment equipments.</span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><b><span lang="EN-US">Computer Technology</span></b></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">In recent years the Computer and Technology Research Unit has developed lots of new and hi-tech products in this field, such as large diameter measuring equipment; new type sensor; intelligent anti-theft door; computer network system, control system and monitoring system used in industrial production. At present, we are developing the standard software of enterprise information management system and how to put it into present daily use.</span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><b><span lang="EN-US">Electronic Engineering and Communication Engineering</span></b></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">The Electronic Engineering and Communication Engineering Research Unit has a group of experts who are engaged in research and their achievements in scientific research have been utilized. Therefore, they are able to undertake engineering research and development in guidance, control, radar and communication etc.</span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><b><span lang="EN-US">Photoelectricity Technology</span></b></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">The staff in the research unit are trained to research and develop photoelectric products.&nbsp;Many photoelectric products have been developed, such as fiber-optical sensor, optic fiber liquid location instrument, optical electric mutual inductor, and electric fine alert carpet etc.</span></p>', NULL, 909, 1, ''),
(196, 1, 'hrbeu', 8, 'Research Centers and Institutes', '2009-04-30 00:31:45', '2009-04-30 00:31:45', 'hrbeu', 'Research Centers and Institutes', 'Research Centers and Institutes', '<div class="Section1" style="layout-grid:  15.6pt none">\r\n<p align="justify"><b><span lang="EN-US">Navigation Technology and Equipment Institute</span></b></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">The Institute is affiliated to Hachuanda Engineering Technology Designing Institute, and the Navigation Technology and Equipment Institute, and undertakes&nbsp; research involved in the development of shipping navigation system and installations. We have developed a comprehensive marine navigation console desk, nautical track instrument, platform compass etc. which have been widely used on various ships and vessels. The basic research, pre-research and technology innovation force of marine navigation discipline in HEU have provided great promotion to the institute.</span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><b><span lang="EN-US">Power Equipment Engineering Technology Institute of HEU (PEETI)</span></b></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">We are committed to engage in the development, researching, manufacturing, and installation and service for the relevant products of HEU College of Power and Energy Engineering.<img height="148" hspace="10" src="http://english.hrbeu.edu.cn/Research/pic/02.jpg" width="243" align="right" vspace="10" border="1" alt="" /></span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">Power Equipment Engineering Technology Institute of HEU is affiliated to Hachuanda Engineering Technology Institute. A selection of the programs of the College of Power and Energy Engineering such as internal combustion engine, gas turbine engine, nuclear power were founded at Harbin Military Engineering Academy in 1950s and have an important influence on the domestic shipping power field. </span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">PEETI is undertaken many shipping industry research programs for the sake of national defense in the past years and have obtained a batch of important achievements, many of which are being utilized on products such as simulated/digital electronic speed governor, successive pressurized controller, oil consumption instrument, exhaust and noise elimination device, cool noise elimination device, and seawater silencer. The Institute''s research have financial support of around 30 million yuan from the ''211 Project'' and Special Project, and the scientific research conditions have been greatly improved and have made considerable progress.</span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><b><span lang="EN-US">Beisa Marine Equipment and Installation Institute</span></b></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">Beisa Marine Equipment and Installation Institute is one of the fruitful institutes of HEU. It is engaged in the research, development and production of shipping and power control equipment and system and has been for the last 30 years. </span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">The main research directions are: shipping dynamic positioning, submersible and underwater robot control, shipping dynamic equipment monitoring etc. </span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">With the great support of State Planning Commission and the Commission of Science and Technology of National Defense Industry, the Institute has been able to develop the first developed shipping dynamic positioning technique and has formed a series of products. The dynamic positioning system that was installed on certain ROV working source-ship was evaluated internationally as the first-invented. The first surface ship dynamic positioning system, under the support of which the domestically biggest double ''</span>I<span lang="EN-US">'' shape submersible designed by HEU has a completed cable-controlling underwater salvage procedure. Shipping dynamic positioning products developed by the Institute have be approved by the ISO9001 quality system. The Institute has become an important production and research base. The automatic control equipments on the man-carrying deep diving submersible are products from this Institute. </span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">Beisa Marine Equipment and Installation Institute has got a batch of achievements in shipping dynamic equipment monitoring, nuclear power installation monitoring and simulation. At present there are 3 professors and 4 associate professors who have considerable experience in theory and engineering practice and also are up-to-date with recent and future technology development trend. The Institute have trained and are training more than 30 master students and candidates and more than 20 doctoral students. </span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><b><span lang="EN-US">Great Wall Underwater Hi-Tech Co. Harbin R&amp;D Center</span></b></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">Jointly set up by HEU and Lanzhou Great Wall Electrical Engineering Group, and Great Wall Underwater Hi-Tech Co. Harbin R&amp;D Center makes efforts in R&amp;D of various underwater hi-tech products. At present their main product are Dam Safety Monitoring Robot subsidiary programs are Nondestructive Blood Sugar Testing Instrument, and Underwater Cleaning Robot, etc.</span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">The Dam Safety Monitoring Robot is the first hi-tech integration developed for dam safety monitoring. Different types of acoustic, light, electric sensing systems will be equipped on robots. Through information synthesizing in these systems, diagnosis and quality monitoring of dangerous situations for reservoirs and dams can be performed. This synthetical hi-tech product is the transformation of long-term technical accumulation in underwater field by HEU. Its further development will help to create continued contributions to national economy and the military industry.</span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="en-us"><b>The following lists the remaining research institutes/centers in the Hi-tech Park</b></span><b><span lang="EN-US">:</span></b></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">HEU Shipping Anti-rolling and Control Technique Institute,</span></p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">HEU Energy Engineering Technology Institute, </span></p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">Intelligence Control Institute,</span></p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">Marine Intelligent Machinery Institute, </span></p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">Ruibai Information Network Institute, </span></p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">Chemistry and New Material Institute,</span></p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">Thermal Energy Engineering Technology Institute,</span></p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">Nuclear Power Installations Institute, </span></p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">Purification Science Institute,</span></p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">New Chemical Technique Institute, </span></p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">Ship and Vessel Material Technique Institute,</span></p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">Naval Vessel and Artillery Technology Institute,</span></p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">Guided Missile Engineering Institute,</span></p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">Turbine Engineering Applied Technology Institute,</span></p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">Underwater Acoustic Technique Institute, </span></p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">Purification and Separation Technology Institute.</span></p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">Center of High Dependability Computing Technology</span></p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">Information Security Research Center</span></p>\r\n    </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>', NULL, 876, 1, ''),
(197, 1, 'hrbeu', 8, 'Main Research Achievements since the 10th "Five-Year Plan"', '2009-04-30 00:32:14', '2009-04-30 00:32:14', 'hrbeu', 'Main Research Achievements since the 10th "Five-Year Plan"', 'Main Research Achievements since the 10th "Five-Year Plan"', '<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US"><b>The II Type Submersible</b>:</span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">combined navigation, electronic marine chart, anti-roller, falling-supporting with light, platform compass, grain depot automation, fingerprint identification system, strip and belt detector, underwater ballistic gauging system, audio-visual information processing and understanding</span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><b><span lang="en-us">Our Commitment:</span></b></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">After years of development, HEU has formed the principle of developing by unique features, and has established a developing strategic orientation of depending on shipping, facing national economy construction. It will continue to make more efforts in scientific research in the coming years and become a university focusing in research.</span></p>', NULL, 856, 1, ''),
(198, 1, 'hrbeu', 8, 'Key Disciplines', '2009-04-30 00:32:42', '2009-04-30 00:32:42', 'hrbeu', 'Key Disciplines', 'Key Disciplines', '<p><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 11pt">State Key Academic Disciplines</span></b></p>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li><font style="font-size: 11pt"><span lang="EN-US">Underwater Acoustic Engineering</span></font></li>\r\n    <li><font style="font-size: 11pt"><span lang="EN-US">Ship and Ocean Structure Designing and Manufacture</span></font></li>\r\n    <li><font style="font-size: 11pt"><span lang="EN-US">Navigation, Guidance and Control</span></font></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<p><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 11pt">National Defense Key Academic Disciplines</span></b></p>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li><font style="font-size: 11pt"><span lang="EN-US">Solid Mechanics</span></font></li>\r\n    <li><font style="font-size: 11pt"><span lang="EN-US">Navigation, Guidance and Control</span></font></li>\r\n    <li><font style="font-size: 11pt"><span lang="EN-US">Ship and Ocean Structure Designing and Manufacture</span></font></li>\r\n    <li><font style="font-size: 11pt"><span lang="EN-US">Turbine Engine Engineering</span></font></li>\r\n    <li><font style="font-size: 11pt"><span lang="EN-US">Underwater Acoustic Engineering</span></font></li>\r\n    <li><font style="font-size: 11pt"><span lang="EN-US">Nuclear Energy Science and Engineering</span></font></li>\r\n    <li><font style="font-size: 11pt"><span lang="EN-US">Radiation Protection and Environment Protection</span></font></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<p><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 11pt">Ministry-Level Key Academic Disciplines</span></b></p>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li><font style="font-size: 11pt"><span lang="EN-US">Underwater Acoustic Engineering</span></font></li>\r\n    <li><font style="font-size: 11pt"><span lang="EN-US">Ship and Ocean Engineering Fluid Mechanics</span></font></li>\r\n    <li><font style="font-size: 11pt"><span lang="EN-US">Ship and Ocean Engineering Structural Mechanics</span></font></li>\r\n    <li><font style="font-size: 11pt"><span lang="EN-US">Turbine Engine Engineering</span></font></li>\r\n    <li><font style="font-size: 11pt"><span lang="EN-US">Ship and Ocean Engineering Special Subsidiary Device and System</span></font></li>\r\n    <li><font style="font-size: 11pt"><span lang="EN-US">Inertia Technology and its Navigation Equipment</span></font></li>\r\n    <li><font style="font-size: 11pt"><span lang="EN-US">Solid Mechanics</span></font></li>\r\n    <li><font style="font-size: 11pt"><span lang="EN-US">Management Engineering</span></font></li>\r\n    <li><font style="font-size: 11pt"><span lang="EN-US">Mechanics</span></font></li>\r\n    <li><font style="font-size: 11pt"><span lang="EN-US">Communication and Electronic System</span></font></li>\r\n    <li><font style="font-size: 11pt"><span lang="EN-US">Computer Application</span></font></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<p><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 11pt">Provincial Key Academic Disciplines</span></b></p>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li><font style="font-size: 11pt"><span lang="EN-US">Acoustics</span></font></li>\r\n    <li><font style="font-size: 11pt"><span lang="EN-US">Aviation Cosmos Propulsion Theory and Engineering</span></font></li>\r\n    <li><font style="font-size: 11pt"><span lang="EN-US">Computer Software and Theory</span></font></li>\r\n    <li><font style="font-size: 11pt"><span lang="EN-US">Testing Technique and Automatic Device</span></font></li>\r\n    <li><font style="font-size: 11pt"><span lang="EN-US">Power Electronics and Power Transmission</span></font></li>\r\n    <li><font style="font-size: 11pt"><span lang="EN-US">Pattern Identification and Intelligence System</span></font></li>\r\n    <li><font style="font-size: 11pt"><span lang="EN-US">Dynamic Mechanics and Engineering</span></font></li>\r\n    <li><font style="font-size: 11pt"><span lang="EN-US">Materials</span></font></li>\r\n    <li><font style="font-size: 11pt"><span lang="EN-US">Applied Chemistry</span></font></li>\r\n    <li><font style="font-size: 11pt"><span lang="EN-US">Signal and Information Processing</span></font></li>\r\n    <li><font style="font-size: 11pt"><span lang="EN-US">Nuclear Energy Science and Engineering</span></font></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', NULL, 826, 1, ''),
(199, 1, 'hrbeu', 8, 'National Science Park Of HEU', '2009-04-30 00:33:06', '2009-04-30 00:33:06', 'hrbeu', 'National Science Park Of HEU', 'National Science Park Of HEU', '<div class="Section1" style="layout-grid:  15.6pt none">\r\n<p align="justify"><b><span lang="EN-US">Our Commitment</span></b></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">We are committed to developing and establishing a first-class national park. These efforts are shown through the continual readjustment of the industrial structure of the Park and the development of its research area and department resources. ''Explore new technology and enhance lives''</span><span lang="EN-US"> is the eternal theme for the development of the National Science Park of HEU is the eternal theme for the development of the National Science Park of HEU.</span></p>\r\n<p align="justify">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div align="center"><img height="150" src="http://english.hrbeu.edu.cn/Administration_and_Service_Departments/pic/bu1.jpg" width="306" border="1" alt="" /></div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align="justify"><b><span lang="EN-US">Brief</span></b></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">the National Science Park of HEU was established in 2000 with the support of the National Science and Technology Committee and Harbin municipal government. It is one of 44 national universities, with a science park with a gross investment of 600 million yuan and takes up an area of 7. 60,000 m<sup>2</sup> among which the construction area is 300,000 m<sup>2</sup>. </span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">The Park is an important contribution to new technological achievements conversion base and a new city development key area and technological innovation base. HEU Science Park is one that incorporates research and development of modern technology, hatching of the new high-tech enterprises and cultivating innovative talents is a primary aim of the Park as a whole.</span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><b><span lang="EN-US">Research and Development</span></b></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">A complete working system has been set up to give the Park a wide area of expertise: including a service center, network center, trade center of the scientific and technological products, financing center, commercial service center, software research and development center and a postdoctoral scientific research mobile station.</span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">the National Science Park of HEU pays attention to high quality teaching, and scientific research, and also is interested in knowledge-intensive, intelligence-intensive, strong financing ability advantages. Through researching and developing, the Park has now achieved a good scientific and technological environment. This includes a relaxed atmosphere, at the same time forming the hi-tech industry group and become the cradle in which new high-tech enterprises grow up and entrepreneurs are cultivated.</span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><b><span lang="EN-US">Training Center</span></b></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">The Park has reached an agreement with Microsoft (China) Co., Ltd. and has become the 4<sup>th</sup>&nbsp; domestic ''Microsoft Cooperative Partner'', therefore a Microsoft Authorized Training Center (ATC) is now organized. Authorized by U.S.A. NCS Company, the software centre in the Hi-tech Park will set up VUE International Test Centre which gears to the needs of the society and undertakes many types of advanced technological authenticating examinations. </span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">The U.S. Pacific Ocean Scientific &amp; Technical (China) Co. is also working with the Hi-tech Park and preparing to establish software LINUX operating system to help development of teaching and training.</span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">The Park utilizes technology and talents the University can continue to expand the business of the software training center. The launching of online long-range education, it hopes to widen business to other large and medium cities in the province and plays a critical role in promoting science in this regional area of China and beyond.</span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="en-us"><b>Future Plan</b></span><b><span lang="EN-GB">s</span></b></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">The future of the Park looks at flowing efforts in training of technical talents, and knowledge assurance for the development of the Science Park. Large-scale training centers in the Park provide all kinds of extra-curricular cultural classes and artistic specialty classes for more than 1200 personages and surrounding residents. There are 10-13 large/medium/small-sized multimedia classrooms which can hold up to 800-1000 people at a same time. </span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">We sincerely look forward to your joining, and wish to make progress together with you.</span></p>', NULL, 833, 1, ''),
(200, 1, 'hrbeu', 8, 'Post-doctoral Scientific Research', '2009-04-30 00:33:29', '2009-04-30 00:33:29', 'hrbeu', 'Post-doctoral Scientific Research', 'Post-doctoral Scientific Research', '<div class="Section1" style="layout-grid:  15.6pt none">\r\n<p align="justify"><b><span lang="EN-US">Postdoctoral R&amp;D Bases</span></b></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">Since 1985 China began to establish postdoctoral R&amp;D bases. Receiving supports from various lines in China, the program is developing at a fast speed. This program is an important base for senior academic experts and scholars cultivation, which has great realistic and far-reaching indication to speed up the training of high level talents, strengthen the academic exchange and scientific research. It is also of great importance to promote education, R&amp;D, economic and social development of China.</span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><b><span lang="EN-US">Postdoctoral R&amp;D Bases of HEU Graduate School</span></b></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">At present, HEU Graduate School has 9 Postdoctoral R&amp;D Bases, as following:</span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">The Postdoctoral R&amp;D Base of Architecture and Ocean Engineering </span></p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">The Postdoctoral R&amp;D Base of Mechanics</span></p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">The Postdoctoral R&amp;D Base of Control Science and Engineering</span></p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">The Postdoctoral R&amp;D Base of Management Science and Technology</span></p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">The Postdoctoral R&amp;D Base of Computer Science and Technology</span></p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">The Postdoctoral R&amp;D Base of Information and Telecommunication Engineering</span></p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">The Postdoctoral R&amp;D Base of Power Engineering and Engineering Thermophysics</span></p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">The Postdoctoral R&amp;D Base of Mechanics Engineering</span></p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">The Postdoctoral R&amp;D Base of Material Science and Technology</span></p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">The Postdoctoral R&amp;D Base of Nuclear Science and Technology</span></p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">The Postdoctoral R&amp;D Base of Instrument Science and Technology</span></p>\r\n    </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p align="justify"><b><span lang="EN-US">Postdoctoral Work Station under National Science Park of HEU </span></b></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">In October, 2002 National Science Park of HEU was the only one science park in China to be approved of establishing its postdoctoral work station. It regards knowledge, respect talents, foster new hi-tech enterprises and entrepreneurs along with training and bringing up highly qualified personnel as important priorities. With rich capital strength, a solid technological foundation, talent resources of innovation and practical strength. The pleasant working environment, favorable settlement grants and rewards act as&nbsp; incentive measures, to encourage the appeal to potential staff and students and create good research conditions. Staff are provided with benefits on living, children education, and housing etc. This is extended to postdoctoral researchers in order to promote and develop postdoctoral research work strategically. The building-up of postdoctoral work station is striving to produce a comfortable and efficient working system and living environment. </span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">In line with the ''open competition, select the best applicants'' principle, postdoctors are recruited in a transparent way through fair competition, so as to ensure&nbsp; the development of high-level, quality and efficiency of postdoctoral scientific research. The famous experts and scholars of HEU, relying on the support and help of the University, which provides a support of fund, technology and research. The Park''s development is aimed at providing an efficient environment to promote theoretical and practical research. The research practiced here includes: electronic information technology, life sciences and biotechnology, modern communication technology, optical, mechanical and electronic integration technology, material science, new material technology, new energy, ecological science and technology and medical technology of environmental protection, etc. The research station lives on the idea that science and technology is ''pursuing excellence'', and promotes the development of the University and enterprises helping construct a brand-new platform bringing progress in this new hi-tech industry. </span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><b><span lang="EN-US">Our Commitments</span></b></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">We are committed not only to create conditions for the fast development of the Science Park by recruiting and training of talented personnel to strengthen the scientific and technological innovation ability of the Park but to introduce all kinds of senior specialized personnel to new ideas to help make positive contributions for the promotion to scientific and technological progresses.</span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">The Bases/Station condenses the research abilities of the University and society as a whole to help form a scientific research security system in which to show the world and face the future. WE sincerely welcomes both domestic and international doctors, to come join us to create beautiful tomorrow!</span></p>\r\n</div>', NULL, 885, 1, ''),
(201, 1, 'hrbeu', 8, 'Graduate School', '2009-04-30 00:35:31', '2009-04-30 00:35:31', 'hrbeu', 'Graduate School', 'Graduate School', '<p><strong>Introduction</strong><br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\nGraduate School of Harbin Engineer University was amongst the first universities who were given with authorization right of master''s and doctor''s degrees who were given, which makes our university one out of fifty five universities with graduate schools. Since 1978, the graduate education available of the College is constantly growing. Nowadays, there are more than 5,500 post-graduate students in registry, and more than 9 postdoctoral R&amp;D bases around the University.</p>\r\n<p>The Graduate School is in charge postdoctoral R&amp;D bases, 5 doctoral research centers of first-level disciplines, 22 doctoral research centers of second-level disciplines, 60 master''s degree programs, 1 MBA program and 18 professional master of engineering&nbsp; programs.</p>\r\n<p>The School always tries to maintain the work ethnic of ''high efficiency, high-quality and creativity''. In 1978 and 1984 it started to enroll master graduate and doctor graduate respectively, the number of enrollment of graduate has developed from 8 to 4000 now. Additionally, there are also more than 500 furtherly educated students. Up to now, the University has trained more than 3000 masters, and 200 doctors. Since 1989 when the Postdoctoral R&amp;D Base founded, more than 50 postdoctors have joined the Base, and most of whom have become the backbone of the teaching and scientific research field.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Our Mission<br />\r\n</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\nThe School has always maintained the following mindset that education: quality is the lifeline of graduate education with creativity as the soul of education. It insists to create on the basis of feature and strength the feature in creation. According to the developing strategy (specializing in shipping industry, serving the national defense, and the national economy) of the University, the School conduct scientific research along with refined and high quality teachings the students are brought to the frontier of scientific training.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Functions</strong><br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\nThe School is a functional department of enrollment, teaching organization and management, degree authorization for doctor and master candidates, project master candidates,MBA candidates and etc., and of postdoctor management.</p>\r\n<p>The School is divided into two sections: Management Section and Training Section. Management Section includes Administration Office and Admission Office; Training Section includes Training Office and Degree Management Office.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Administration Office</strong><br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\nThe Office is taking charge of HEU postdoctoral R&amp;D bases and administration on postdoctors, including, entrance examination, monitoring program implementation, funds, qualification examination, funds application, and administration on all HEU postgraduate students, including, registry record management and scholarships granting.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Admission Office</strong><br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;in charge of:</p>\r\n<p>promotion for postgraduate student enrollment;</p>\r\n<p>postgraduate student registry and record management;</p>\r\n<p>academic performance evaluation for postgraduate students.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Training Office</strong><br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\nin charge of :</p>\r\n<p>organizing and amending of the graduate training program;</p>\r\n<p>administrating postgraduate curriculum arrangement;</p>\r\n<p>administrating graduate curriculum (part-time) management;</p>\r\n<p>administrating prizes for postgraduate students.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Degree Management Office&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong><br />\r\nin charge of:</p>\r\n<p>administrating postgraduate students'' thesis/dissertation writing;</p>\r\n<p>administrating graduation and degree granting for postgraduates and the granting of bachelor degree;</p>\r\n<p>establishing and implementing the discipline evaluating system;</p>\r\n<p>organizing and selecting advisors and tutors for postgraduate students;</p>\r\n<p>publicizing academicians appointment information, and recommending candidates for the Evaluating Section of the State Council''s Degree Committee.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Contact us</strong><br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\n<table id="table3" height="178" width="100%" border="1">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td width="158"><b><font face="Times New Roman" size="2">Dean</font></b></td>\r\n            <td colspan="2"><font face="Times New Roman" size="2"><span lang="EN-US">Prof. Yang Desen</span></font></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td width="158"><b><font face="Times New Roman" size="2"><span lang="EN-US">Executive deputy dean</span></font></b></td>\r\n            <td width="124"><span lang="en-us"><font face="Times New Roman" size="2">0086 451 82519678</font></span></td>\r\n            <td rowspan="2">\r\n            <p align="center" style="line-height: 18pt; text-align: left"><font face="Times New Roman" size="2"><span lang="EN-US">Room 715, Administration Building</span></font></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td width="158" height="19"><b><font face="Times New Roman" size="2"><span lang="EN-US">Deputy dean</span></font></b></td>\r\n            <td width="124" height="19"><span lang="en-us"><font face="Times New Roman" size="2">0086 451 82518910</font></span></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td width="158"><b><font face="Times New Roman" size="2">Administration Office</font></b></td>\r\n            <td width="124"><font face="Times New Roman" size="2"><span lang="EN-US">0086 451 82519825</span></font></td>\r\n            <td rowspan="2"><font face="Times New Roman" size="2"><span lang="EN-US">Room 731, Administration Building</span></font></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td width="158"><b><span lang="en-us"><font face="Times New Roman" size="2">Admission</font></span><font face="Times New Roman" size="2"><span lang="EN-US"> office</span></font></b></td>\r\n            <td width="124"><span lang="en-us"><font face="Times New Roman" size="2">00</font></span><font face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US"><font size="2">86 451 82519679 </font></span></font></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td width="158"><b><span lang="en-us"><font face="Times New Roman" size="2">T</font></span><font face="Times New Roman" size="2"><span lang="EN-US">raining office</span></font></b></td>\r\n            <td width="124"><span lang="en-us"><font face="Times New Roman" size="2">00</font></span><font face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US"><font size="2">86 451 82519872 </font></span></font></td>\r\n            <td rowspan="2">\r\n            <p style="line-height: 18pt"><font face="Times New Roman" size="2"><span lang="EN-US">Room 720, Administration Building</span></font></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td width="158">\r\n            <p style="line-height: 18pt"><b><font face="Times New Roman" size="2">Degree management office</font></b></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width="124"><font face="Times New Roman" size="2">0086 451 82519841</font></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>', NULL, 861, 1, ''),
