(204, 1, 'hrbeu', 8, 'Foreign Affairs Office', '2009-04-30 00:38:26', '2009-04-30 00:38:26', 'hrbeu', 'Foreign Affairs Office', 'Foreign Affairs Office', '<p><span style="font-family: Arial"><strong>Introduction:<br />\r\n&nbsp;</strong><br />\r\nForeign Affairs Office of Harbin Engineering University is a department, which manages and serves the University''s foreign cooperation and exchange work.&nbsp; The Office is responsible for implementing national foreign policies and higher authority departments to help guide and coordinate the university''s external affairs. The function of the Office is to enhance the international reputation of the University in all aspects, including teaching, scientific research, industrial development, and rear service. It serves to also recruit experienced students and employees from foreign countries to help enhance the strength of the academic departments of the University. The main functions can be generalized as the follows:</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial">managing and assisting international collaborations</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial">organizing&nbsp; international exchanges</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial">organizing international lectures/seminars/conferences, etc.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial">procedure for long/short term travels abroad handle for both students and University staff.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial">enrolling and organizing foreign students and foreign affairs.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial"><strong>Sections:</strong><br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\nInternational Communications</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial">&nbsp;in charge of :</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial">inviting, reception, arranging and organizing of the visiting foreign guests;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial">communicating for and implementing international exchange programs; </span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial">examining, and issuing approvals for the academic departments'' application to host international conferences, and coordinating international conferences held at HEU;&nbsp; </span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial">examining and issuing approvals for international visits, and issuing approvals of all official foreign business, including: application management of the passport and visa paperwork etc.&nbsp; </span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial">managing international exchange programs with other academic institutions. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial">International Students </span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial">&nbsp;in charge of :</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial">enrollment of foreign students, and management of foreign students'' register record;&nbsp; </span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial">management of foreign students'' passports and visas;&nbsp; </span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial">administration of&nbsp; foreign students;&nbsp; </span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial">logistics support for the foreign student apartment;&nbsp; </span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial">international training item;&nbsp; </span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial">establishing the study abroad center.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial">Administration&nbsp; Section</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial">&nbsp;in charge of :</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial">recruiting and coordinating foreign experts;&nbsp; </span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial">applying for and administrating short- and long-term program funds from the State Administration on Foreign Experts Affairs and the Chinese Commission of Science, Commission of Science Technology and Industry for National Defense;&nbsp; </span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial">applying for and administrating the Hong Kong and