(206, 1, 'hrbeu', 10, 'Our Scenarios', '2009-04-30 00:40:12', '2009-04-30 00:40:12', 'hrbeu', 'Our Scenarios', 'Our Scenarios', '<p align="justify"><b><span lang="EN-US">Collaboration and Development of the Software Industry</span></b></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">The National Science Park of HEU relies primarily on utilizing university talents, who have a access to information, and technology facilities to help develop technical software. The main research focuses on application software products of artificial technology, including virtual imitation technology, civil GPS navigate synthetically and data integration technology, etc.&nbsp; The department has already made some huge advances in technological innovation. The Hi-tech Park has set a priority to support information-based projects represented by ERP, PDM and SCM, and offers omni-directional technical support for information-based projects of Heilongjiang Province. </span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><b><span lang="EN-US">New Companies</span></b></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US"><img height="194" hspace="10" src="http://english.hrbeu.edu.cn/Business/pic/OurScenarios.jpg" width="327" align="left" vspace="10" border="1" alt="" />The National Science Park of HEU has already started 23 scientific and technological companies which take shape with a gross output value of these companies already exceeding 200,000,000 yuan RMB. The formation of an industrial cluster taking Development Co., Ltd. as a gathering into investing or participating by shares. The Park will carry on a shareholding system transformation according to the modern enterprise''s mode to encourage growth in the next 1-2 years. In a few years, it is predicted that the Park will train a number of outstanding companies with annual output exceeding 50,000,000 yuan RMB, making them the pillar companies of the Park.</span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="en-us"><b>Developing Scientific and Industrial Achievements</b></span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">The Park extends its research range to cover vertical industry through foster research and development and use a trade advantage, to establish the hardware necessary for environment industrialized development. The department is currently working on building software and high-new products production base in the Xinle Community of Taiping district in Harbin, and also all to assist Harbin in becoming industry on Yingbin Road in the Development Zone, of an industrialized platform which promotes scientific and technical results to transform and connect with the market directly. The establishment of the production base can also advance the process of industrialization of scientific and technical result of the park, and make the Nation Science Park of Harbin Engineer University become the base of modern technology and cultivation based on new hi-tech enterprise.</span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="en-us"><b>Designing </b></span><b><span lang="EN-US">Software</span></b></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">The Park has 65 incubated companies now; including many software companies and there are also many software-tapping talents at and around the University with all kinds of software. At present, the software products developed by domestic software companies lacks a quality guarantee. Through the Park''s own investigation, this lack of quality control is due to many reasons industry smaller software companies financial resource restriction etc., lacking qualified and adequate technical staff, also quality assessments are also inadequate. </span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">An effective way of solving above-mentioned problems is to build the public software development test platform of the Park, which not only include a software developing platform but also a software test platform. The software-developing platform will offer the open software development an opportunity to test the efficiency of the software for the Park. It also help to promote innovative project, with skilled personnel who can start an undertaking, medium and small software design businesses, inside and outside the province. The public development and test platform of software can continue software, but through test also insure quality of the software project. This will in turn economize on time, cost, personnel and resource.</span></p>', NULL, 898, 1, ''),
(207, 1, 'hrbeu', 10, 'Achievements', '2009-04-30 00:40:35', '2009-04-30 00:40:35', 'hrbeu', 'Achievements', 'Achievements', '<p align="justify" style="line-height: 150%"><span lang="EN-US">The incubator of the National Science Park of HEU is constantly&nbsp; perfecting and strengthening its software and hardware facilities and environmental construction constantly. At present, including the incubator, the total Park area (including the incubator) cover 70,000m<sup>2</sup>. Through the cooperation with Personnel Department of Heilongjiang Province, the Provincial Aboard-studying Personnel''s Pioneer Park and Longjiang Post-doctor Apartment Building have been built within the Park. A key construction project in Heilongjiang Province; the main part of the national level ''Software Center of Harbin'' was set up in the Park too. </span></p>\r\n<p align="justify" style="line-height: 150%"><span lang="EN-US">The Park takes in 30-50 companies to the park every year, and also creates 10-20 companies. The Park is trying to make 10 companies graduate every year in the following three years with annual output up to 3,000,000 yuan RMB at least.</span></p>\r\n<p align="justify" style="line-height: 150%"><span lang="EN-US">In 2006 the Center hopes to expand both in size and its service available industry; training service, business service, business service, commerce consultation, risk financing, legal consultation, patent agent of commercial affairs, etc. are offered. Out of the 80,000m<sup>2 </sup></span>involved in this complex, 30,000<span lang="EN-US">m<sup>2</sup></span>&nbsp; <span lang="EN-US">will be used for scientific and technological advancement. </span></p>\r\n<p align="justify" style="line-height: 150%"><span lang="EN-US">The creation of new projects within the Park hopes to reach 80, including 5 of which conducted by graduates. The future&nbsp; is bright with already a gross output reaches 1,500,000,000yuan RMB gross income of technology, project and trade reaches 2 billion yuan RMB. It will realize profit tax of 100,000,000 yuan RMB, and will offer the employment opportunities of 3,000 people for society. </span></p>', NULL, 899, 1, ''),
