(215, 1, 'hrbeu', 11, 'Graduate School', '2009-04-30 00:47:39', '2009-06-30 10:23:56', 'hrbeu', 'Graduate School', 'Graduate School', '<p style="text-align: right"><strong><a href="http://yjsy.hrbeu.edu.cn/">Graduate School Homepage</a></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Introduction</strong><br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\nGraduate School of Harbin Engineer University was amongst the first universities who were given with authorization right of master''s and doctor''s degrees who were given, which makes our university one out of fifty five universities with graduate schools. Since 1978, the graduate education available of the College is constantly growing. Nowadays, there are more than 5,500 post-graduate students in registry, and more than 9 postdoctoral R&amp;D bases around the University.</p>\r\n<p>The Graduate School is in charge postdoctoral R&amp;D bases, 5 doctoral research centers of first-level disciplines, 22 doctoral research centers of second-level disciplines, 60 master''s degree programs, 1 MBA program and 18 professional master of engineering&nbsp; programs.</p>\r\n<p>The School always tries to maintain the work ethnic of ''high efficiency, high-quality and creativity''. In 1978 and 1984 it started to enroll master graduate and doctor graduate respectively, the number of enrollment of graduate has developed from 8 to 4000 now. Additionally, there are also more than 500 furtherly educated students. Up to now, the University has trained more than 3000 masters, and 200 doctors. Since 1989 when the Postdoctoral R&amp;D Base founded, more than 50 postdoctors have joined the Base, and most of whom have become the backbone of the teaching and scientific research field.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Our Mission</strong><br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\nThe School has always maintained the following mindset that education: quality is the lifeline of graduate education with creativity as the soul of education. It insists to create on the basis of feature and strength the feature in creation. According to the developing strategy (specializing in shipping industry, serving the national defense, and the national economy) of the University, the School conduct scientific research along with refined and high quality teachings the students are brought to the frontier of scientific training.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Functions</strong><br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\nThe School is a functional department of enrollment, teaching organization and management, degree authorization for doctor and master candidates, project master candidates,MBA candidates and etc., and of postdoctor management.</p>\r\n<p>The School is divided into two sections: Management Section and Training Section. Management Section includes Administration Office and Admission Office; Training Section includes Training Office and Degree Management Office.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Administration Office</strong><br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\nThe Office is taking charge of HEU postdoctoral R&amp;D bases and administration on postdoctors, including, entrance examination, monitoring program implementation, funds, qualification examination, funds application, and administration on all HEU postgraduate students, including, registry record management and scholarships granting.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Admission Office</strong><br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;in charge of:</p>\r\n<p>promotion for postgraduate student enrollment;</p>\r\n<p>postgraduate student registry and record management;</p>\r\n<p>academic performance evaluation for postgraduate students.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Training Office</strong><br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\nin charge of :</p>\r\n<p>organizing and amending of the graduate training program;</p>\r\n<p>administrating postgraduate curriculum arrangement;</p>\r\n<p>administrating graduate curriculum (part-time) management;</p>\r\n<p>administrating prizes for postgraduate students.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Degree Management Office&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong><br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\nin charge of:</p>\r\n<p>administrating postgraduate students'' thesis/dissertation writing;</p>\r\n<p>administrating graduation and degree granting for postgraduates and the granting of bachelor degree;</p>\r\n<p>establishing and implementing the discipline evaluating system;</p>\r\n<p>organizing and selecting advisors and tutors for postgraduate students;</p>\r\n<p>publicizing academicians appointment information, and recommending candidates for the Evaluating Section of the State Council''s Degree Committee.</p>\r\n<p><span lang="EN-US"><strong>Contact us</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span lang="EN-US">\r\n<table id="table3" height="178" width="100%" border="1">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td width="158"><b><font face="Times New Roman" size="2">Dean</font></b></td>\r\n            <td colspan="2"><font face="Times New Roman" size="2"><span lang="EN-US">Prof. Yang Desen</span></font></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td width="158"><b><font face="Times New Roman" size="2"><span lang="EN-US">Executive deputy dean</span></font></b></td>\r\n            <td width="124"><span lang="en-us"><font face="Times New Roman" size="2">0086 451 82519678</font></span></td>\r\n            <td rowspan="2">\r\n            <p align="center" style="line-height: 18pt; text-align: left"><font face="Times New Roman" size="2"><span lang="EN-US">Room 715, Administration Building</span></font></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td width="158" height="19"><b><font face="Times New Roman" size="2"><span lang="EN-US">Deputy dean</span></font></b></td>\r\n            <td width="124" height="19"><span lang="en-us"><font face="Times New Roman" size="2">0086 451 82518910</font></span></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td width="158"><b><font face="Times New Roman" size="2">Administration Office</font></b></td>\r\n            <td width="124"><font face="Times New Roman" size="2"><span lang="EN-US">0086 451 82519825</span></fon