(217, 1, 'hrbeu', 11, 'Personnel Office', '2009-04-30 00:48:35', '2009-06-30 10:25:26', 'hrbeu', 'Personnel Office', 'Personnel Office', '<p style="text-align: right"><b><a href="http://hr.hrbeu.edu.cn/">Office Homepage</a></b></p>\r\n<p><b>Personnel Administration Section</b></p>\r\n<p>in charge of:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>personnel allocation and recruitment for the University</li>\r\n    <li>talent and graduate recruitment and follow-up arrangement</li>\r\n    <li>staff performance appraisal, discipline and punishment</li>\r\n    <li>University staff information collection and management</li>\r\n    <li>personnel file management</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><b>Faculty Administration Section</b></p>\r\n<p>in charge of:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>technical professionals management and appraisal</li>\r\n    <li>the University staff training fund management, and the training application examine and approval</li>\r\n    <li>selection, report and management on candidates involved in the University or government training program</li>\r\n    <li>examine, approval and management on private overseas programs</li>\r\n    <li>technical processional post management</li>\r\n    <li>concurrent professors and staff management</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><b>Salary and Insurance Section</b></p>\r\n<p>in charge of:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>annual salary schedule, report and management</li>\r\n    <li>subsidiary, pension and allowance management</li>\r\n    <li>social mutual assistance program management</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><b>Contact us:</b></p>\r\n<div align="center">\r\n<table id="table1" width="62%" border="1">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td width="209"><b><font size="2"><span lang="EN-GB">Director</span></font></b></td>\r\n            <td><span lang="en-gb"><font size="2">0086 451 82519965</font></span></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td width="209"><b><font size="2"><span lang="EN-GB">Personnel Administration Section</span></font></b></td>\r\n            <td><font size="2"><span lang="EN-GB">0086 451 82519854</span></font></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td width="209"><b><font size="2">Personnel Working Section</font></b></td>\r\n            <td><font size="2">0086 451 82518061</font></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td width="209"><b><font size="2">Administration Section</font></b></td>\r\n            <td><font size="2">0086 451 82519253</font></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td width="209"><b><font size="2">Faculty Administration Section</font></b></td>\r\n            <td><font size="2">0086 451 82519752</font></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td width="209"><b><font size="2">Salary and Insurance Section</font></b></td>\r\n            <td><font size="2">0086 451 82519751</font></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td width="209"><span lang="en-gb"><b><font size="2">Personnel Affairs Representing Section</font></b></span></td>\r\n            <td><font size="2"><span lang="EN-GB">0086 451 82519</span></font><span lang="en-gb"><font size="2">553</font></span></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>', NULL, 916, 1, ''),
(218, 1, 'hrbeu', 11, 'National Science Park of HEU', '2009-04-30 00:49:03', '2009-06-30 10:27:23', 'hrbeu', 'National Science Park of HEU', 'National Science Park of HEU', '<div class="Section1" style="layout-grid:  15.6pt none">\r\n<p style="text-align: right"><b><span lang="EN-US"><a href="http://www.heusp.com/">Nationa Science Park Homepage</a></span></b></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><b><span lang="EN-US">Our Commitment</span></b></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">We are committed to developing and establishing a first-class national park. These efforts are shown through the continual readjustment of the industrial structure of the Park and the development of its research area and department resources. ''Explore new technology and enhance lives''</span><span lang="EN-US"> is the eternal theme for the development of the National Science Park of HEU is the eternal theme for the development of the National Science Park of HEU.</span></p>\r\n<p align="justify">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div align="center"><img height="150" alt="" width="306" border="1" src="http://english.hrbeu.edu.cn/Administration_and_Service_Departments/pic/bu1.jpg" /></div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align="justify"><b><span lang="EN-US">Brief</span></b></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">the National Science Park of HEU was established in 2000 with the support of the National Science and Technology Committee and Harbin municipal government. It is one of 44 national universities, with a science park with a gross investment of 600 million yuan and takes up an area of 7. 60,000 m<sup>2</sup> among which the construction area is 300,000 m<sup>2</sup>. </span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">The Park is an important contribution to new technological achievements conversion base and a new city development key area and technological innovation base. HEU Science Park is one that incorporates research and development of modern technology, hatching of the new high-tech enterprises and cultivating innovative talents is a primary aim of the Park as a whole.</span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><b><span lang="EN-US">Research and Development</span></b></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">A complete working system has been set up to give the Park a wide area of expertise: including a service center, network center, trade center of the scientific and technological products, financing center, commercial service center, software research and development center and a postdoctoral scientific research mobile station.</span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">the National Science Park of HEU pays attention to high quality teaching, and scientific research, and also is interested in knowledge-intensive, intelligence-intensive, strong financing ability advantages. Through researching and developing, the Park has now achieved a good scientific and technological environment. This includes a relaxed atmosphere, at the same time forming the hi-tech industry group and become the cradle in which new high-tech enterprises grow up and entrepreneurs are cultivated.</span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><b><span lang="EN-US">Training Center</span></b></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">The Park has reached an agreement with Microsoft (China) Co., Ltd. and has become the 4<sup>th</sup>&nbsp; domestic ''Microsoft Cooperative Partner'', therefore a Microsoft Authorized Training Center (ATC) is now organized. Authorized by U.S.A. NCS Company, the software centre in the Hi-tech Park will set up VUE International Test Centre which gears to the needs of the society and undertakes many types of advanced technological authenticating examinations. </span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">The U.S. Pacific Ocean Scientific &amp; Technical (China) Co. is also working with the Hi-tech Park and preparing to establish software LINUX operating system to help development of teaching and training.</span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">The Park utilizes technology and talents the University can continue to expand the business of the software training center. The launching of online long-range education, it hopes to widen business to other large and medium cities in the province and plays a critical role in promoting science in this regional area of China and beyond.</span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="en-us"><b>Future Plan</b></span><b><span lang="EN-GB">s</span></b></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">The future of the Park looks at flowing efforts in training of technical talents, and knowledge assurance for the development of the Science Park. Large-scale training centers in the Park provide all kinds of extra-curricular cultural classes and artistic specialty classes for more than 1200 personages and surrounding residents. There are 10-13 large/medium/small-sized multimedia classrooms which can hold up to 800-1000 people at a same time. </span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">We sincerely look forward to your joining, and wish to make progress together with you.</span></p>', NULL, 901, 1, ''),
