(220, 1, 'hrbeu', 11, 'Network Information Center', '2009-04-30 00:49:57', '2009-06-30 10:29:25', 'hrbeu', 'Network Information Center', 'Network Information Center', '<p style="text-align: right"><b><span lang="EN-US"><a href="http://nic.hrbeu.edu.cn/">Center Homepage</a></span></b></p>\r\n<p><b><span lang="EN-US">Introduction:</span></b></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">The Network Information Center of Harbin Engineering University was established in March 2001 and now has 29 permanent staff now. It is divided into the following sections: network section, modern education technology section, communication section and administration section. The Network Information Center is responsible for operating and managing the network technology, developing and applying the networked digital teaching of modern educational technology, securing, operating, and managing campus communication technology and synthetically manages multimedia classroom and meeting district. </span></p>\r\n<p><b><span lang="EN-US">Network Section:</span></b></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">The Comprehensive Computer Information Network on campus was established in September of 1995. It was interconnected with CERNET, INTERNET and realized office automation of the network service on campus. In 2001,HEU and China Telecom United to establish the digital broadband network on campus. The first-phase project constructed 5000 ports, reached 1000M in the main cable and 10M bandwidth to the screen. </span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">The construction of the digital broadband network on campus will better solve the output problem of the campus network systems. Campus comprehensive computer information network plays an important role in realizing resource-sharing, office automation on the campus, and interconnecting with CERNET and INERTNET. </span></p>\r\n<p><b><span lang="EN-US">Modern Education Technology Section:</span></b></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">The Modern Education Technology Section is one of many transaction units which use new technologies integrated with educational skills and education media information. The section''s development is focusing on modernization, informationization and internationalization. Multimedia and networked information is one effective means for digitized teaching, researching the basic theories of teaching, enlarging environment, collecting and creating resources, and making good use of various studying tools. This section aims to strengthen the ability of teaching course information and serves for the modernization and internationalization of the educational development.</span></p>\r\n<p><b><span lang="EN-US">Communication Section:</span></b></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">The Communication Section is responsible for the normal running of the digital program-controlled switchboard of the campus, and maintaining four network systems on campus (telephone networks, cable television networks, broadband digital networks, campus computer networks). This section not only helps to solve network problems for end users but also offers the services for network account consulting.</span></p>\r\n<p><span lang="en-us" style="font-weight: 700">Administration</span><font style="font-weight: 700"><span lang="EN-US"> Section:</span></font></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">The Administration Section is responsible for daily management of the multimedia lecture rooms, Shaw Building and meeting venues. At present there are 18 multimedia classrooms that can hold more than 260 audience. These classrooms have been all equipped with the modern multimedia teaching systems such as the advanced large screen projector and multimedia computer etc. in order to promote the modernization of teaching at HEU.</span></p>\r\n<p><font style="font-weight: 700"><span lang="EN-GB">Contact us:</span></font></p>\r\n<div align="center">\r\n<table id="table1" width="83%" border="1">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td width="148" rowspan="2"><b><span lang="en-us"><font size="2">Director</font></span></b></td>\r\n            <td><span lang="en-us"><font size="2">0086 451 82518555</font></span></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><span lang="en-us"><font size="2">0086 451 82568222 (Fax)</font></span></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td width="148"><b><font size="2"><span lang="EN-US">Administration Section</span></font></b></td>\r\n            <td><font size="2"><span lang="EN-US">0086 451 82518222</span></font></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td width="148"><b><font size="2"><span lang="EN-GB">Location</span></font></b></td>\r\n            <td><span lang="EN-US"><font size="2">Rm 405, Shaw Building, Harbin Engineering University</font></span></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>', NULL, 877, 1, '');
