(288, 1, 'hrbeu', 33, 'Bachelor in Automation', '2009-05-02 06:06:09', '2009-05-02 06:06:09', 'hrbeu', 'Bachelor in Automation', 'Bachelor in Automation', '<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US"><b>Introduction: </b>We are committed to cultivate senior engineers specializing in system analysis, design, and operation, technological development and research in the fields of locomotion control, industrial process control, electrical power and electronic technology, measuring technology and automation equipments, electronic and computer technology, information processing and management and decision-making. </span>This Program is also open for international students.</p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US"><b>Major benefits for students:</b> The students of this Program are expected to</span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">grasp well-knit natural science and humanities theory, and English, </span></p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">understand the basic technical knowledge well and extensively, including theory of electronic circuit, electronic technology, control theory, information processing, computer hardware, software and application, location control, industrial process control, automation instrument, electric power and electronic technology, etc, </span></p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">receive professional engineering training to enhance the ability of system analysis, design and development. </span></p>\r\n    </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p align="justify"><b><span lang="EN-GB">Graduates'' career prospects:</span></b><span lang="EN-US"> Graduates of this Program always start their career in electric power and electronic enterprises, petrochemical industry</span>,<span lang="EN-US"> telecommunication, traffic services, navigation, shipbuilding, aviation, spaceflight and national defense and other enterprises related with automation and computer technology. The graduates can work at system analysis, design, and operation, scientific development and research in the fields of locomotion control, industrial process control, electrical power and electronic technology, measuring technology and automation equipment, electronic and computer technology, information processing and administration and decision-making.</span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US"><b>Core classes:</b> electronic circuit theory, base of electronic technology, computer principles and application, technical base of computer software, electric power and electronic technology, control theory, computer control system, artificial intelligent generality, etc.</span></p>', NULL, 143, 1, '');
