(289, 1, 'hrbeu', 33, 'Bachelor in Aviation Technology', '2009-05-02 06:06:39', '2009-05-02 06:06:39', 'hrbeu', 'Bachelor in Aviation Technology', 'Bachelor in Aviation Technology', '<div class="Section1" style="layout-grid:  15.6pt none">\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="en-us"><b>Introduction</b></span><b><span lang="EN-US">: </span></b><span lang="EN-US">There lies very expansive development space in the civil aviation market in China. The rapid development of economy in the next decade will drive the development of general aviation, particularly the international cooperation in economy and technology. With the development of the aviation industry, there are great demands for pilots, especially for helicopter pilots. In the context, this Program is established and are committed to cultivate senior engineers specializing in air dynamics, principle of flight, performance and manipulation of flight. </span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="en-us"><b>Major benefits for students</b></span><b><span lang="EN-US">: </span></b><span lang="EN-US">The students are expected to </span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">grasp basic knowledge and principles in operation, aero engine and aircraft repairing technology; </span></p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">master the skills of modern flight and pilot and have the primary ability to drive a flight and pilot; </span></p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">know about the laws and rules of air traffic control and flight safety; </span></p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">know about the development trends of flight technology; </span></p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">have high ability of computer and foreign language application plus excellent presentation, communication, negotiation and management skills; </span></p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">grasp the methods of literature retrieve and data query; </span></p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">have primary ability of scientific research and practical work.</span></p>\r\n    </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US"><b>Graduates'' career prospects:</b> The graduates of this Program are always working for air companies and governments. They work for national traffic ministry, and counter-strike, fire protection, chasing escaped criminals for national police ministry, and forest fire protection for forest sectors, etc.</span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US"><b>Core classes</b>: principle of flight, aircraft structure, aero engine, airborne electronic assembly, aircraft auto-flight, aviation pilot, aviation weather, system repairing, flight safety, crew resource management, engineering mechanics, electrical technology and electrical engineering, land air dialog, aviation gym, etc. </span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US"><b>Core training classes</b>: drills, engineering cognition, engineering training, repairing practice of aircraft system and components, ground preparation practice, flight training, etc.</span></p>\r\n</div>', NULL, 133, 1, ''),
(290, 1, 'hrbeu', 33, 'Bachelor in Biomedical Engineering', '2009-05-02 06:07:01', '2009-05-02 06:07:01', 'hrbeu', 'Bachelor in Biomedical Engineering', 'Bachelor in Biomedical Engineering', '<p align="justify"><span lang="en-us"><b>Introduction</b></span><b><span lang="EN-US">: </span></b><span lang="EN-US">Biomedical Engineering is a comprehensive discipline combining modern life sciences and medical engineering. It is a new technology involved in the fields of applied physics, chemistry, electronics and computer science. It applies engineering methods to research and new problems in the fields of biology and medicine. This Program is committed to cultivate senior engineers specializing in the fields of electronics, computer informatics, medical instruments and life sciences, etc. </span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><b><span lang="EN-US">Core classes:</span></b><span lang="EN-US">&nbsp; theory of electronic circuit, principle and application of computer, foundation of computer software technology, signal and linear systems, digital signal processing, digital medical image processing, medical sensors, detection and instruments of biologic information, biochemistry and engineering physiology, etc.</span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="en-us"><b>Major benefits for students</b></span><b><span lang="EN-US">: </span></b><span lang="EN-US">Students of this program are expected to</span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">master well-knit natural science, humanities, social science and administrative science theory, and English; </span></p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">grasp extensive foundation theory and skills including electronics, computer informatics, medical instruments and life sciences; </span></p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">know about the frontiers of theory and development trends of the subject; </span></p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">have certain ability of scientific research.</span></p>\r\n    </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US"><b>Graduates'' career prospects:</b> Graduates of this Program will be engaged in the departments of scientific research and production, biomedical engineering rooms of big hospitals, and work at researches and developments of biomedicine, iatrical instruments and detection of biologic information. They can also be engaged in the fields of electronic technology, computer technology and information industry.</span></p>', NULL, 110, 1, ''),
(291, 1, 'hrbeu', 33, 'Bachelor in Detection, Guidance and Control Technology', '2009-05-02 06:07:37', '2009-05-02 06:07:37', 'hrbeu', 'Bachelor in Detection, Guidance and Control Technology', 'Bachelor in Detection, Guidance and Control Technology', '<div class="Section1" style="layout-grid:  15.6pt none">\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="en-us"><b>Introduction</b></span><b><span lang="EN-US">: </span></b><span lang="EN-US">We are committed to cultivate senior engineers specializing in the fields of detection, recognition, tracking, positioning of targets and environments, guidance and control, mechanical and electric control, and detection of sensors. </span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US"><b>Major benefits for students: </b>The students are expected to</span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">grasp basic theory and knowledge of mechanics, electronics and control science; </span></p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">master the principles of arm detection, guidance and control, methods of system analysis and design, and technology of developing products; </span></p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">have the ability to solve engineering problems by using computer and devices; </span></p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">know about the frontiers of theory, application foregrounds and development trends of weapon detection, guidance and control; </span></p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">grasp the methods of literature retrieve and data query; </span></p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">has certain ability of scientific research and practical work; </span></p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">know the technical economic and national defense constructional policies and laws very well.</span></p>\r\n    </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US"><b>Graduates'' career prospects:</b> The graduates of this Program are always engaged in national martial services, enterprises and R&amp;D centers in aviation, spaceflight and marine navigation and other related fields. They can also do technical development, experimental testing, and analysis, research and design in the area of detection, guidance and control technology, and other aspects related with the technology.</span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="en-us"><b>Core</b></span><b><span lang="EN-US"> classes:</span></b><span lang="EN-US"> mechanical and electric system design, modern control theory, principles and systems of guidance and control, sensor and testing technology, pattern recognition and intelligent control, GPS and anti-jamming technology, analysis and design of guidance and control systems, detection and recognition technology, system modeling and simulation technology, principle and application of computer, etc.</span></p>\r\n</div>', NULL, 108, 1, ''),
(292, 1, 'hrbeu', 33, 'Bachelor in Electrical Engineering and its Automation', '2009-05-02 06:08:09', '2009-05-02 06:08:09', 'hrbeu', 'Bachelor in Electrical Engineering and its Automation', 'Bachelor in Electrical Engineering and its Automation', '<div class="Section1" style="layout-grid:  15.6pt none">\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="en-us"><b>Introduction</b></span><b><span lang="EN-US">: </span></b><span lang="EN-US">We are committed to cultivate senior engineers specializing in system operation, auto-control, electric power and electronic technology, information processing, experimental analysis, research and development, economic management and the jobs related with electronic and computer technical application. </span>This Program is also open for international students.</p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US"><b>Major benefits for students: </b>The students are expected to</span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">master well-knit natural science, humanities, social science and administrative science theory, and English; </span></p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">systematically grasp technical theory; </span></p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">receive professional engineering practical training; </span></p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">can skillfully use computers to solve applied problems. </span></p>\r\n    </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p align="justify"><b><span lang="EN-US">Graduates'' career prospects:</span></b><span lang="EN-US">&nbsp; The graduates can start their career in R&amp;D centers, universities and colleges, electric power services and factories. They can also work at systems operation, auto-control, electric power and electronic technology, information processing, experimental analysis, research and development, economic management and the jobs related with electronic and computer technical application.</span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="en-us"><b>Core</b></span><b><span lang="EN-US"> classes:</span></b><span lang="EN-US">&nbsp; electronic circuit theory, electric power and electronic technology, computer technology (language, primary theory of software and hardware, Single Chip Micyoco, etc.), signal and systems, control theory, electric machines, electrical towage and control, etc.</span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', NULL, 188, 1, ''),
(293, 1, 'hrbeu', 33, 'Bachelor in Measuring and Control Technology and Instruments', '2009-05-02 06:09:51', '2009-05-02 06:09:51', 'hrbeu', 'Bachelor in Measuring and Control Technology and Instruments', 'Bachelor in Measuring and Control Technology and Instruments', '<p align="justify"><span lang="en-us"><b>Introduction</b></span><b><span lang="EN-US">: </span></b><span lang="EN-US">We are committed to cultivate senior engineers specializing in precision instrument production, and measuring.</span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US"><b>Major benefits for students: </b>The students are expected to</span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">systematically grasp technical theory; </span></p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">receive professional engineering training and possess the ability of system analysis, design, development and research; </span></p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">have the ability of experimental research on modern measuring and control technology which integrates mechanics, electronics and computer; </span></p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">be able to design and develop measuring and control technology, instruments and systems in the field of this subject; </span></p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p align="justify"><span lang="EN-US">master well-knit natural science, humanities, art and social science theory, and practiced English.</span></p>\r\n    </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p align="justify"><b><span lang="EN-US">Graduates'' career prospects: </span></b><span lang="EN-US">The graduates always work in the production enterprises, and research and design centers in the fields of aviation, spaceflight, marine and other departments related with measuring and control. </span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><b><span lang="EN-US">Core classes:</span></b><span lang="EN-US">&nbsp; electronic design of precision machines and instruments, basic theory of digital electronic technology, principle and application of microcomputer, control theory, digital signal processing, and precision measuring and control and system, etc.</span></p>', NULL, 51, 1, ''),
(294, 1, 'hrbeu', 33, 'Master in Biomedical Engineering', '2009-05-02 06:10:30', '2009-05-02 06:10:30', 'hrbeu', 'Master in Biomedical Engineering', 'Master in Biomedical Engineering', '<p align="justify"><span style="font-family: Arial"><b>Introduction: </b><span lang="EN-US" style="color: black">Biomedical engineering is a multidisciplinary discipline of natural science, engineering and medicine. The structure, function, and various life phenomena of people''s body are studied in different levels based on the principle and method of nature science and modern engineering technology. The main applications include the researches on materials, productions, instruments and systems for prevention, diagnosis, nursing, treatment, health care, health procreation, rehabilitation from diseases, et al.</span></span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span style="font-family: Arial"><span lang="EN-US" style="color: black">The aim of this Program is training high-level professional talents. The students must master the fundamental knowledge of life sciences, electronic technology, computer technology, informatics, and possess the scientific research ability of merging medicine and engineering technology. In addition, they will be familiar with the advanced technology and method of biomedical informatics, biomedical signal processing, biomedical image processing, designing and repairing of advanced biomedical instruments, the development of medical computer program, hospital modern information management and telemedicine, and be able to undertake researching, designing, teaching and managing in the field of biomedical, medical instrument and other electronic technology, computer technology, information industry and biology technology.</span></span></p>\r\n<p align="justify"><span style="font-family: Arial"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="color: black">Research Fields</span><span style="color: black">:</span></b></span></p>\r\n<ol style="font-family: Times New Roman">\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p class="MsoNormal" align="justify" style="text-indent: 8.9pt; margin: 0cm 5.25pt 0pt 35.25pt"><span style="font-family: Arial"><span lang="EN-US" style="color: black">Medical Image Processing and Analysis</span> </span></p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p class="MsoNormal" align="justify" style="text-indent: -18pt; margin: 0cm 5.25pt 0pt 60pt"><span style="font-family: Arial"><span lang="EN-US" style="color: black">Organization Engineering and Biomechanics</span> </span></p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p class="MsoNormal" align="justify" style="text-indent: -18pt; margin: 0cm 5.25pt 0pt 60pt"><span style="font-family: Arial"><span lang="EN-US" style="color: black">Human Body Information Examination Technique</span> </span></p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p class="MsoNormal" align="justify" style="text-indent: -18pt; margin: 0cm 5.25pt 0pt 60pt"><span style="font-family: Arial"><span lang="EN-US" style="color: black">Hospital Network Information Management and Telemedicine Technique</span> </span></p>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n    <p class="MsoNormal" align="justify" style="text-indent: -18pt; margin: 0cm 5.25pt 0pt 60pt"><span style="font-family: Arial"><span lang="EN-US" style="color: black">DNA Chip and Application</span> </span></p>\r\n    </li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p align="justify"><span style="font-family: Arial"><span lang="en-us" style="font-weight: 700">Core classes: </span><span lang="EN-US" style="color: black">Specialty Literature Reading, Specialty Chinese, Computer Graphics, Digital Image Processing, Modern Mathematical Foundation in Pattern Reorganization, Computer Vision, Wavelet Theory and Applications, Neural Network Technology, Volume Graphics, Molecule Biology </span></span></p>', NULL, 60, 1, ''),
(295, 1, 'hrbeu', 33, 'Master in Control Theory and Control Engineering', '2009-05-02 06:11:05', '2009-05-02 06:11:05', 'hrbeu', 'Master in Control Theory and Control Engineering', 'Master in Control Theory and Control Engineering', '<div class="Section1" style="layout-grid:  15.6pt none">\r\n<p align="justify" style="line-height: 18pt"><b><span lang="EN-US">Introduction: </span></b><span lang="EN-US">The discipline of Control Theory and Control Engineering is a key discipline of HEU. There are many research fields in this discipline. An important feature of the discipline is the interaction between theoretical studies and realistic constraints of industrial problems. </span>The classes of this Program can be lectured in English.</p>\r\n<p align="justify" style="line-height: 18pt"><b><span lang="EN-US">The main research fields: </span></b><span lang="EN-US">Theory and Application of Robust Control Systems, Ship Movement Control, Intelligent Control, Intelligent Robot Technology, Inertial Navigation Technology, Marine Stabilized Gyro Compass etc. In application, many techniques such as ship motion control, rolling reducing control, ship''s dynamical positioning, the ship electrical propeller control and adaptive autopilot rudder have been applied on many kinds of ships. </span></p>\r\n<p align="justify" style="line-height: 18pt"><b><span lang="EN-US">Research fields</span>:</b></p>\r\n<p align="justify" style="line-height: 18pt"><span lang="EN-US">(1) Theory and Application of Robust Control System <br />\r\n(2) Guidance and Control of Aircraft<br />\r\n(3) Intelligent Control<br />\r\n(4) Neural Network Theory and Application<br />\r\n(5) Ship Movement Control<br />\r\n(6) Digital Image Procession<br />\r\n(7) Adaptive Control <br />\r\n(8) Three-Dimensional Reconstruction<br />\r\n(9) Pattern Recognition<br />\r\n(10) Digital Image Procession and Computer Vision<br />\r\n(11) Intelligent Control Theory and Application <br />\r\n(12) Intelligent Robot Technology<br />\r\n(13) Marine Stabilized Gyro Compass <br />\r\n(14) Inertial Navigation Technology<br />\r\n(15) GPS Technology<br />\r\n</span><b><span lang="EN-US">Core classes</span>: </b><span lang="EN-US">Linear System Theory,&nbsp; Optimal Estimation, Optimization Theory, Chinese Language, </span><span lang="EN-US" style="color: black">Specialty Literature Reading, Adaptive Control, Stochastic Control Theory, Computer Control, Digital Signal Processing, Ship Movement and Models, Ship Manipulation and Control, Hydraulic Control System Design, Specialty Chinese, Process Control, C++ Program Design, Neural Network Control, Variable Structure Control</span></p>\r\n</div>', NULL, 59, 1, ''),
